(353, '2008', 'like_card', '{\"ar\": \"WalaOne Subscription Offer\", \"en\": \"WalaOne Subscription Offer\"}', '{\"ar\": \"A WalaOne Subscription provides users with direct access to exclusive off ers and discounts within the app for a specific ed duration, activated through a unique subscription code.\", \"en\": \"A WalaOne Subscription provides users with direct access to exclusive off ers and discounts within the app for a specific ed duration, activated through a unique subscription code.\"}', '{\"ar\": \"1- Receive a code from your service provider.2- Open the Walaa One app and select \\\"Recharge Points.\\\"3- Enter the code in the \\\"Walaa One Voucher\\\" field to activate your subscription and automatically unlock offers.4- Enjoy all the benefits of your subscription during the subscription period.\", \"en\": \"1- Receive a code from your service provider.2- Open the Walaa One app and select \\\"Recharge Points.\\\"3- Enter the code in the \\\"Walaa One Voucher\\\" field to activate your subscription and automatically unlock offers.4- Enjoy all the benefits of your subscription during the subscription period.\"}', '{\"ar\": \"1- Validity: Valid for one year from the activation date.2- Non-Refundable: The voucher or subscription cannot be exchanged for cash.3- Non-Transferable: The voucher or subscription is for the beneficiary&apos;s personal use and may not be sold or transferred.4- Use in App Only: The voucher or subscription can only be used within the Walaa app and within the Kingdom of Saudi Arabia.5- Offer Conditions: Offers are subject to partner availability and may change without notice.6- Cancellation: Walaa reserves the right to cancel the voucher or subscription in case of misuse without compensation.7- Modifications: Walaa reserves the right to modify or discontinue the product at any time.8- Liability: Walaa is not liable for loss or theft of vouchers or unauthorized use.9- Governing Law: These terms and conditions are governed by the laws of the Kingdom of Saudi Arabia.\", \"en\": \"1- Validity: Valid for one year from the activation date.2- Non-Refundable: The voucher or subscription cannot be exchanged for cash.3- Non-Transferable: The voucher or subscription is for the beneficiary&apos;s personal use and may not be sold or transferred.4- Use in App Only: The voucher or subscription can only be used within the Walaa app and within the Kingdom of Saudi Arabia.5- Offer Conditions: Offers are subject to partner availability and may change without notice.6- Cancellation: Walaa reserves the right to cancel the voucher or subscription in case of misuse without compensation.7- Modifications: Walaa reserves the right to modify or discontinue the product at any time.8- Liability: Walaa is not liable for loss or theft of vouchers or unauthorized use.9- Governing Law: These terms and conditions are governed by the laws of the Kingdom of Saudi Arabia.\"}', 352, '2026-04-09 08:41:54', '2026-04-06 11:06:11', '2026-04-09 08:41:54'),
(354, '2009', 'like_card', '{\"ar\": \"WalaOne Points Voucher\", \"en\": \"WalaOne Points Voucher\"}', '{\"ar\": \"The WalaOne Points Voucher allows users to top up their wallet with loyalty points that can be used across multiple models inside the app, such as Unlocking exclusive off ers and discounts, redeeming digital shopping vouchers, converting points to flight miles or investment options, Using them as a payment method with selected partners.\", \"en\": \"The WalaOne Points Voucher allows users to top up their wallet with loyalty points that can be used across multiple models inside the app, such as Unlocking exclusive off ers and discounts, redeeming digital shopping vouchers, converting points to flight miles or investment options, Using them as a payment method with selected partners.\"}', '{\"ar\": \"1- Receive the coupon code from the vouchers section.2- Log in to your existing account or create a new one.3- Open the Walaa One app and select \\\"Recharge Points.\\\"4- Enter the code in the \\\"Walaa One Coupon\\\" field to automatically top up your wallet.\", \"en\": \"1- Receive the coupon code from the vouchers section.2- Log in to your existing account or create a new one.3- Open the Walaa One app and select \\\"Recharge Points.\\\"4- Enter the code in the \\\"Walaa One Coupon\\\" field to automatically top up your wallet.\"}', '{\"ar\": \"1- Validity: Valid for one year from the activation date.2- Non-Refundable: The voucher or subscription cannot be exchanged for cash.3- Non-Transferable: The voucher or subscription is for the beneficiary&apos;s personal use and may not be sold or transferred.4- Use in App Only: The voucher or subscription can only be used within the Walaa app and within the Kingdom of Saudi Arabia.5- Offer Conditions: Offers are subject to partner availability and may change without notice.6- Cancellation: Walaa reserves the right to cancel the voucher or subscription in case of misuse without compensation.7- Modifications: Walaa reserves the right to modify or discontinue the product at any time.8- Liability: Walaa is not liable for loss or theft of vouchers or unauthorized use.9- Governing Law: These terms and conditions are governed by the laws of the Kingdom of Saudi Arabia.\", \"en\": \"1- Validity: Valid for one year from the activation date.2- Non-Refundable: The voucher or subscription cannot be exchanged for cash.3- Non-Transferable: The voucher or subscription is for the beneficiary&apos;s personal use and may not be sold or transferred.4- Use in App Only: The voucher or subscription can only be used within the Walaa app and within the Kingdom of Saudi Arabia.5- Offer Conditions: Offers are subject to partner availability and may change without notice.6- Cancellation: Walaa reserves the right to cancel the voucher or subscription in case of misuse without compensation.7- Modifications: Walaa reserves the right to modify or discontinue the product at any time.8- Liability: Walaa is not liable for loss or theft of vouchers or unauthorized use.9- Governing Law: These terms and conditions are governed by the laws of the Kingdom of Saudi Arabia.\"}', 352, '2026-04-09 08:41:54', '2026-04-06 11:06:11', '2026-04-09 08:41:54'),
(355, '2029', 'like_card', '{\"ar\": \"FxTweet\", \"en\": \"FxTweet\"}', '{\"ar\": \"FX Tweet is a rapidly growing platform that delivers high-confidence investment signals, empowering traders with timely, data-driven insights to make informed trading decisions.\", \"en\": \"FX Tweet is a rapidly growing platform that delivers high-confidence investment signals, empowering traders with timely, data-driven insights to make informed trading decisions.\"}', '{\"ar\": \"1- Click on the following link:https://topup.skarla.com/Topup/5?source=skarla2- Enter your email address.3- Enter the voucher code, then click Redeem.\", \"en\": \"1- Click on the following link:https://topup.skarla.com/Topup/5?source=skarla2- Enter your email address.3- Enter the voucher code, then click Redeem.\"}', NULL, NULL, '2026-04-09 08:41:54', '2026-04-06 11:06:11', '2026-04-09 08:41:54'),
(356, '1793', 'like_card', '{\"ar\": \"Sala Entertainment\", \"en\": \"Sala Entertainment\"}', '{\"ar\": \"SALA Entertainment is a subsidiary of Veda Holding in Saudi Arabia that specializes in entertainment for all ages to create unforgettable immersive experiences. SALA Entertainment started its journey to entertain the local community and families in 2012, with the first Billy Beez branch. Since then it expanded its offering with brands such as Sala City, Karting, Laser tag, KidZania, Billy Beez, BOB&apos;s Famous, and Sala Metaverse, with over 36 facilities across the Kingdom.\\\\n\", \"en\": \"SALA Entertainment is a subsidiary of Veda Holding in Saudi Arabia that specializes in entertainment for all ages to create unforgettable immersive experiences. SALA Entertainment started its journey to entertain the local community and families in 2012, with the first Billy Beez branch. Since then it expanded its offering with brands such as Sala City, Karting, Laser tag, KidZania, Billy Beez, BOB&apos;s Famous, and Sala Metaverse, with over 36 facilities across the Kingdom.\\\\n\"}', '{\"ar\": \"Buy the ticket from LikeCard → Receive the code → Go to the branch → Show the code to the cashier to redeem. \", \"en\": \"Buy the ticket from LikeCard → Receive the code → Go to the branch → Show the code to the cashier to redeem. \"}', '{\"ar\": \"For more detailes, visit our site https://salaentertainment.com/ \", \"en\": \"For more detailes, visit our site https://salaentertainment.com/ \"}', NULL, '2026-04-09 08:41:54', '2026-04-06 11:06:11', '2026-04-09 08:41:54'),
(357, '1990', 'like_card', '{\"ar\": \"Grandiose\", \"en\": \"Grandiose\"}', '{\"ar\": \"Grandiose is a premier quality food & grocery retailer that delivers a memorable multisensory experience and best in class service in a unique grocery shopping environment.\", \"en\": \"Grandiose is a premier quality food & grocery retailer that delivers a memorable multisensory experience and best in class service in a unique grocery shopping environment.\"}', '{\"ar\": \"- How to Redeem Gift Card Offline1- Visit your nearest Grandiose store.2- Shop your favourite items.3- Present your gift card at the billing counter.4- The gift card value will be applied, and you can complete your billing.- How to Redeem Gift Card Online1- Log in to your Grandiose mobile app.2- Add products to your cart and proceed to checkout.3- On the payment page, select the option Redeem Gift Card.4- Enter your gift card details to redeem.\", \"en\": \"- How to Redeem Gift Card Offline1- Visit your nearest Grandiose store.2- Shop your favourite items.3- Present your gift card at the billing counter.4- The gift card value will be applied, and you can complete your billing.- How to Redeem Gift Card Online1- Log in to your Grandiose mobile app.2- Add products to your cart and proceed to checkout.3- On the payment page, select the option Redeem Gift Card.4- Enter your gift card details to redeem.\"}', '{\"ar\": \"1- The Gift Cards shall be redeemable at Grandiose physical/Digital stores across the UAE.2-  The Gift Cards have an expiry period and shall be valid for 1 Year from the date ofactivation.3-  Gift Cards cannot be exchanged for Cash and/or Cheques.4-  Partial redemption of the Gift Card is allowed, and the balance will remain in the GiftCard.5-  In case of a damaged Gift Card, a new Gift Card will be issued by the Gift Card Issuer tothe end customer.6-  If the Gift Card is stolen or lost, neither will a new Gift Card be issued nor will themoney be reimbursed in any manner.7-  Balance information on a Gift card could be obtained by visiting any Grandiose physicalstores or during checkout process on Grandiose app/ website. 8- Provider email address for support in case there is an issue with the coderajat.arora01@pinelabs.com\", \"en\": \"1- The Gift Cards shall be redeemable at Grandiose physical/Digital stores across the UAE.2-  The Gift Cards have an expiry period and shall be valid for 1 Year from the date ofactivation.3-  Gift Cards cannot be exchanged for Cash and/or Cheques.4-  Partial redemption of the Gift Card is allowed, and the balance will remain in the GiftCard.5-  In case of a damaged Gift Card, a new Gift Card will be issued by the Gift Card Issuer tothe end customer.6-  If the Gift Card is stolen or lost, neither will a new Gift Card be issued nor will themoney be reimbursed in any manner.7-  Balance information on a Gift card could be obtained by visiting any Grandiose physicalstores or during checkout process on Grandiose app/ website. 8- Provider email address for support in case there is an issue with the coderajat.arora01@pinelabs.com\"}', NULL, '2026-04-09 08:41:54', '2026-04-06 11:06:11', '2026-04-09 08:41:54'),
(358, '1987', 'like_card', '{\"ar\": \"MUSE Gift Card\", \"en\": \"MUSE Gift Card\"}', '{\"ar\": \"MUSE is a luxury loyalty programme across 30+ fashion, beauty and lifestyle brands. Members earn points on every purchase, access exclusive benefits, and unlock personalised rewards in-store and online.\", \"en\": \"MUSE is a luxury loyalty programme across 30+ fashion, beauty and lifestyle brands. Members earn points on every purchase, access exclusive benefits, and unlock personalised rewards in-store and online.\"}', '{\"ar\": \"1- Open the email containing your MUSE Gift Card.2- Visit any participating MUSE brand in-store or online. Click here to learn more: https://giftcards.experience-muse.com/en-ae/redeem3- In-store: Present your gift card barcode or card number at the counter.4- Online: Enter your gift card number at checkout and select “Gift Card” as the payment method.5- Complete your purchase and enjoy shopping and collecting points with MUSE.\", \"en\": \"1- Open the email containing your MUSE Gift Card.2- Visit any participating MUSE brand in-store or online. Click here to learn more: https://giftcards.experience-muse.com/en-ae/redeem3- In-store: Present your gift card barcode or card number at the counter.4- Online: Enter your gift card number at checkout and select “Gift Card” as the payment method.5- Complete your purchase and enjoy shopping and collecting points with MUSE.\"}', '{\"ar\": \"1- The MUSE Gift Card (“Gift Card”) is denominated in United Arab Emirates Dirhams (AED).2- Gift Cards may be purchased through LikeCard, an authorized third-party distributor, and will be delivered digitally to the purchaser’s registered email address once payment is completed.3- Gift Cards are valid for twelve (12) months from the date of issuance, after which they expire automatically. Expired balances cannot be recovered, extended, or refunded.4- Gift Cards are not debit cards, credit cards, bank accounts, cheque guarantee cards, or charge cards.5- Gift Cards cannot be refunded, exchanged for cash, or used to purchase other gift cards. They also cannot be used for cash-on-delivery orders or for products/services excluded at MUSE’s discretion.6- Gift Cards may only be redeemed at participating MUSE brand stores and online platforms located in the United Arab Emirates. Refer to: https://giftcards.experience-muse.com/en-ae/redeem7- When making a purchase, the transaction amount will be deducted from the Gift Card balance.8- If the purchase is less than the balance, the remaining value will remain on the card for future use.9- If the purchase exceeds the balance, the difference must be paid using another accepted payment method.10- Gift Card balances cannot be transferred, merged, or consolidated with other Gift Cards.11- Balances can be checked: · Online at https://giftcards.experience-muse.com/en-ae/balenq12- By contacting MUSE Customer Care at 800 888 77713- Refunds or exchanges for items purchased with a Gift Card are subject to the refund and exchange policy of the respective MUSE brand store.14-  If a refund is approved, a new Gift Card (marked as a “return card”) may be issued for the value of the returned item. The return card will carry the same expiry date and usage rules as the original Gift Card, unless otherwise stated, and will be sent to the customer’s registered email address.15-  MUSE is not liable for unauthorized use of lost or stolen Gift Cards. At its sole discretion and upon purchase verification, MUSE may consider issuing a replacement card. Additional validation steps may apply.16- MUSE reserves the right to amend these Terms and Conditions at any time without prior notice. It may suspend or restrict the use of Gift Cards, make changes to the Gift Card program, or refuse issuance/redemption of a Gift Card if deemed appropriate.17- MUSE may take necessary actions to ensure fraud prevention, regulatory compliance, and operational efficiency.18- These Terms of Use are governed by and construed in accordance with the laws Dubai, United Arab Emirates and disputes shall be subject to the non-exclusive jurisdiction of the competent courts of Dubai, United Arab Emirates.\", \"en\": \"1- The MUSE Gift Card (“Gift Card”) is denominated in United Arab Emirates Dirhams (AED).2- Gift Cards may be purchased through LikeCard, an authorized third-party distributor, and will be delivered digitally to the purchaser’s registered email address once payment is completed.3- Gift Cards are valid for twelve (12) months from the date of issuance, after which they expire automatically. Expired balances cannot be recovered, extended, or refunded.4- Gift Cards are not debit cards, credit cards, bank accounts, cheque guarantee cards, or charge cards.5- Gift Cards cannot be refunded, exchanged for cash, or used to purchase other gift cards. They also cannot be used for cash-on-delivery orders or for products/services excluded at MUSE’s discretion.6- Gift Cards may only be redeemed at participating MUSE brand stores and online platforms located in the United Arab Emirates. Refer to: https://giftcards.experience-muse.com/en-ae/redeem7- When making a purchase, the transaction amount will be deducted from the Gift Card balance.8- If the purchase is less than the balance, the remaining value will remain on the card for future use.9- If the purchase exceeds the balance, the difference must be paid using another accepted payment method.10- Gift Card balances cannot be transferred, merged, or consolidated with other Gift Cards.11- Balances can be checked: · Online at https://giftcards.experience-muse.com/en-ae/balenq12- By contacting MUSE Customer Care at 800 888 77713- Refunds or exchanges for items purchased with a Gift Card are subject to the refund and exchange policy of the respective MUSE brand store.14-  If a refund is approved, a new Gift Card (marked as a “return card”) may be issued for the value of the returned item. The return card will carry the same expiry date and usage rules as the original Gift Card, unless otherwise stated, and will be sent to the customer’s registered email address.15-  MUSE is not liable for unauthorized use of lost or stolen Gift Cards. At its sole discretion and upon purchase verification, MUSE may consider issuing a replacement card. Additional validation steps may apply.16- MUSE reserves the right to amend these Terms and Conditions at any time without prior notice. It may suspend or restrict the use of Gift Cards, make changes to the Gift Card program, or refuse issuance/redemption of a Gift Card if deemed appropriate.17- MUSE may take necessary actions to ensure fraud prevention, regulatory compliance, and operational efficiency.18- These Terms of Use are governed by and construed in accordance with the laws Dubai, United Arab Emirates and disputes shall be subject to the non-exclusive jurisdiction of the competent courts of Dubai, United Arab Emirates.\"}', NULL, '2026-04-09 08:41:54', '2026-04-06 11:06:11', '2026-04-09 08:41:54'),
(359, '1275', 'like_card', '{\"ar\": \"Lifebox Üyelik - TR\", \"en\": \"Lifebox Üyelik - TR\"}', '{\"ar\": \"Lifebox is a cloud storage service that lets you back up all the memories on your phone, including photos, videos, music files, and phone contacts in your gallery. Photos, contacts, and videos from your phone or tablet are automatically uploaded to lifebox and stored securely. You can access your archive via mylifebox at any time, transfer these backed-up contents to your smart device, and share them.\", \"en\": \"Lifebox is a cloud storage service that lets you back up all the memories on your phone, including photos, videos, music files, and phone contacts in your gallery. Photos, contacts, and videos from your phone or tablet are automatically uploaded to lifebox and stored securely. You can access your archive via mylifebox at any time, transfer these backed-up contents to your smart device, and share them.\"}', '{\"ar\": \"To activate the Lifebox codes you purchase through LikeCard, follow the steps below:1- Log in to mylifebox.com.2- Log in if you have a Lifebox membership. Otherwise, create one.3- After logging in to your Lifebox account, click the \\\"My Packages\\\" tab. Then, enter the Lifebox package code you purchased through LikeCard in the \\\"Activate Package Activation Code\\\" section at the bottom.\", \"en\": \"To activate the Lifebox codes you purchase through LikeCard, follow the steps below:1- Log in to mylifebox.com.2- Log in if you have a Lifebox membership. Otherwise, create one.3- After logging in to your Lifebox account, click the \\\"My Packages\\\" tab. Then, enter the Lifebox package code you purchased through LikeCard in the \\\"Activate Package Activation Code\\\" section at the bottom.\"}', '{\"ar\": \"1- The package code included in the email is only valid for the specified amount of storage and duration.2- No refunds will be issued unless required by law.3- Each code can be used once.4- It has no expiration date.5- The code cannot be resold and is for personal use only and cannot be used for commercial purposes.6- Lifecell Bulut Çözümleri A.Ş. is not responsible for lost or stolen cards or unauthorized use.7- You can access all features of lifebox at https://mylifebox.com.8- This product can be used by any mobile operator in Turkey.\", \"en\": \"1- The package code included in the email is only valid for the specified amount of storage and duration.2- No refunds will be issued unless required by law.3- Each code can be used once.4- It has no expiration date.5- The code cannot be resold and is for personal use only and cannot be used for commercial purposes.6- Lifecell Bulut Çözümleri A.Ş. is not responsible for lost or stolen cards or unauthorized use.7- You can access all features of lifebox at https://mylifebox.com.8- This product can be used by any mobile operator in Turkey.\"}', NULL, '2026-04-09 08:41:54', '2026-04-06 11:06:11', '2026-04-09 08:41:54'),
(360, '1276', 'like_card', '{\"ar\": \"Zula - TR\", \"en\": \"Zula - TR\"}', '{\"ar\": \"Zula is the first Turkish-made game in the MMOFPS genre.Zula can be played by registering for free on the official website and downloading it to your computer.There are two enemy factions in the game: the Zula team, formed by former military and intelligence officers, and the Gladyo team, comprised of mercenaries. You can choose to be either Zula or Gladyo. You can join this challenging struggle with your chosen character.The currency used in Zula is called Zula Gold. By purchasing Zula Gold ZA, you can purchase in-game items such as weapons, ammunition, equipment, and more.\", \"en\": \"Zula is the first Turkish-made game in the MMOFPS genre.Zula can be played by registering for free on the official website and downloading it to your computer.There are two enemy factions in the game: the Zula team, formed by former military and intelligence officers, and the Gladyo team, comprised of mercenaries. You can choose to be either Zula or Gladyo. You can join this challenging struggle with your chosen character.The currency used in Zula is called Zula Gold. By purchasing Zula Gold ZA, you can purchase in-game items such as weapons, ammunition, equipment, and more.\"}', '{\"ar\": \"To use the Zula Gold code you purchased from LikeCard, follow these steps:1- Log in to https://hesap.zulaoyun.com/zula-giris-yap.2- Click the \\\"Top Up Your Pin\\\" button.3- Enter the code you purchased from LikeCard into the designated field on the screen and click the \\\"Top Up\\\" button.\", \"en\": \"To use the Zula Gold code you purchased from LikeCard, follow these steps:1- Log in to https://hesap.zulaoyun.com/zula-giris-yap.2- Click the \\\"Top Up Your Pin\\\" button.3- Enter the code you purchased from LikeCard into the designated field on the screen and click the \\\"Top Up\\\" button.\"}', '{\"ar\": \"1- Not valid on the Steam Platform.2- Not valid on Zula Mobile.3- Products are delivered instantly as e-pins after payment is completed.4- Digital products cannot be returned in accordance with the relevant article of the Turkish Commercial Code.\", \"en\": \"1- Not valid on the Steam Platform.2- Not valid on Zula Mobile.3- Products are delivered instantly as e-pins after payment is completed.4- Digital products cannot be returned in accordance with the relevant article of the Turkish Commercial Code.\"}', NULL, '2026-04-09 08:41:54', '2026-04-06 11:06:11', '2026-04-09 08:41:54'),
(361, '1461', 'like_card', '{\"ar\": \"Exxen\", \"en\": \"Exxen\"}', '{\"ar\": \"Founded by Acun Medya, Exxen has been broadcasting since January 1, 2021, with the slogan \\\"Turkey&apos;s digital platform.\\\" Exxen, which allows its members to watch unique content anytime, anywhere, on any device, has over 1 million members.Exxen offers two types of membership: with ads (RKLMVAR) or without ads (RKLMYOK).An Exxen Membership with Ads means that ads are included within the content, while an Exxen Membership Without Ads allows for uninterrupted viewing.\", \"en\": \"Founded by Acun Medya, Exxen has been broadcasting since January 1, 2021, with the slogan \\\"Turkey&apos;s digital platform.\\\" Exxen, which allows its members to watch unique content anytime, anywhere, on any device, has over 1 million members.Exxen offers two types of membership: with ads (RKLMVAR) or without ads (RKLMYOK).An Exxen Membership with Ads means that ads are included within the content, while an Exxen Membership Without Ads allows for uninterrupted viewing.\"}', '{\"ar\": \"To activate the Exxen membership codes you purchase through LikeCard, follow the steps below:1- Go to https://www.exxen.com/tr/settings.2- Click the \\\"Click to use your promo code\\\" field in the \\\"My Membership Information\\\" section.3- Enter the Exxen membership code you purchased from LikeCard in the relevant field and click the \\\"Continue\\\" button.\", \"en\": \"To activate the Exxen membership codes you purchase through LikeCard, follow the steps below:1- Go to https://www.exxen.com/tr/settings.2- Click the \\\"Click to use your promo code\\\" field in the \\\"My Membership Information\\\" section.3- Enter the Exxen membership code you purchased from LikeCard in the relevant field and click the \\\"Continue\\\" button.\"}', '{\"ar\": \"1- Exxen Membership codes are only valid in Türkiye.2- Digital products cannot be returned, in accordance with the relevant article of the Turkish Commercial Code.\", \"en\": \"1- Exxen Membership codes are only valid in Türkiye.2- Digital products cannot be returned, in accordance with the relevant article of the Turkish Commercial Code.\"}', NULL, '2026-04-09 08:41:54', '2026-04-06 11:06:11', '2026-04-09 08:41:54'),
(362, '1358', 'like_card', '{\"ar\": \"TOD - TUR\", \"en\": \"TOD - TUR\"}', '{\"ar\": \"Movies, TV Series, Kids, Documentaries, and much more are in the Entertainment Package!Over 750 Turkish and international HD movies with subtitle and dubbing optionsRepeats of popular TV series you missedThousands of episodes of children&apos;s content for all agesOver 60 TV channelsEasy membership with no installation or commitment!\", \"en\": \"Movies, TV Series, Kids, Documentaries, and much more are in the Entertainment Package!Over 750 Turkish and international HD movies with subtitle and dubbing optionsRepeats of popular TV series you missedThousands of episodes of children&apos;s content for all agesOver 60 TV channelsEasy membership with no installation or commitment!\"}', '{\"ar\": \"To activate the TOD Entertainment codes you purchase through LikeCard, follow these steps:1- Visit www.todtv.com.tr.2- Enter the Coupon Code you receive in the COUPON CODE field at the bottom of the page or by clicking the link www.todtv.com.tr/kupon-kodu.3- Finally, complete the free membership process.4- Once the Coupon Code is activated, the purchased package will be activated immediately and will grant you access to watch the Entertainment Package content for 3 months.5- If the Coupon Code is activated for the TOD Entertainment Package (Web + Mobile + Tablet + Apple TV + Android TV + Smart TV), the relevant content will be available for viewing on www.todtv.com.tr and the TOD mobile apps.6- Content can also be viewed through the Smart TV TOD app.\", \"en\": \"To activate the TOD Entertainment codes you purchase through LikeCard, follow these steps:1- Visit www.todtv.com.tr.2- Enter the Coupon Code you receive in the COUPON CODE field at the bottom of the page or by clicking the link www.todtv.com.tr/kupon-kodu.3- Finally, complete the free membership process.4- Once the Coupon Code is activated, the purchased package will be activated immediately and will grant you access to watch the Entertainment Package content for 3 months.5- If the Coupon Code is activated for the TOD Entertainment Package (Web + Mobile + Tablet + Apple TV + Android TV + Smart TV), the relevant content will be available for viewing on www.todtv.com.tr and the TOD mobile apps.6- Content can also be viewed through the Smart TV TOD app.\"}', '{\"ar\": \"1- To access the content included in your package, you must be a TOD member.2- Package codes are valid for domestic TOD service.3- Package codes cannot be converted to cash, are non-refundable, and are non-transferable.4- Package codes are for single-use only.5- Digiturk reserves the right to change the campaign terms and conditions.6- If you encounter any problems using your coupon code, you can contact chat.digiturk.com.tr/bc/chat/Login.7- Live Customer Service can assist you.\", \"en\": \"1- To access the content included in your package, you must be a TOD member.2- Package codes are valid for domestic TOD service.3- Package codes cannot be converted to cash, are non-refundable, and are non-transferable.4- Package codes are for single-use only.5- Digiturk reserves the right to change the campaign terms and conditions.6- If you encounter any problems using your coupon code, you can contact chat.digiturk.com.tr/bc/chat/Login.7- Live Customer Service can assist you.\"}', NULL, '2026-04-09 08:41:54', '2026-04-06 11:06:11', '2026-04-09 08:41:54'),
(363, '1458', 'like_card', '{\"ar\": \"Wolfteam  Joypara - Turkey Store\", \"en\": \"Wolfteam  Joypara - Turkey Store\"}', '{\"ar\": \"Wolfteam game is an MMOFPS online game about the war of Wolves and Men, developed by Softnyx and published by Joygame in Turkey.\\\\nAt the same time, Joygame, Turkey&apos;s most popular Online FPS game, uses its own balance unit called joypara to enable users to purchase store and market products in its existing games on the market.\\\\n\", \"en\": \"Wolfteam game is an MMOFPS online game about the war of Wolves and Men, developed by Softnyx and published by Joygame in Turkey.\\\\nAt the same time, Joygame, Turkey&apos;s most popular Online FPS game, uses its own balance unit called joypara to enable users to purchase store and market products in its existing games on the market.\\\\n\"}', '{\"ar\": \"How to redeem Wolfteam card:\\\\n1- Log in as a member at www.joygame.com. Then click on the \\\"Load Joy Money\\\" tab.\\\\n2- Click on the \\\"Epin\\\" option from the payment methods.\\\\n3- Enter the code you purchased and click the \\\"Continue\\\" button.\\\\n\", \"en\": \"How to redeem Wolfteam card:\\\\n1- Log in as a member at www.joygame.com. Then click on the \\\"Load Joy Money\\\" tab.\\\\n2- Click on the \\\"Epin\\\" option from the payment methods.\\\\n3- Enter the code you purchased and click the \\\"Continue\\\" button.\\\\n\"}', '{\"ar\": \"1- Products are delivered instantly via e-pin after the payment process is completed.\\\\n2- For digital products, product returns cannot be made in accordance with the relevant article of the Turkish Commercial Code.\\\\n\", \"en\": \"1- Products are delivered instantly via e-pin after the payment process is completed.\\\\n2- For digital products, product returns cannot be made in accordance with the relevant article of the Turkish Commercial Code.\\\\n\"}', NULL, '2026-04-09 08:41:54', '2026-04-06 11:06:11', '2026-04-09 08:41:54'),
(364, '1782', 'like_card', '{\"ar\": \"Black Desert Online\", \"en\": \"Black Desert Online\"}', '{\"ar\": \"Black Desert Online (BDO) is an MMORPG developed by Pearl Abyss, notable for its action-oriented combat system, expansive open world, and detailed character customization. Players explore the open world through dynamic combat and engage in rich economic activities and trade. It also features combat elements such as PvP battles, large-scale group battles, and castle conquests. Visually stunning, BDO offers players detailed character customization options and activities like animal breeding. Overall, it&apos;s a popular choice for those seeking an intense and in-depth gaming experience.\", \"en\": \"Black Desert Online (BDO) is an MMORPG developed by Pearl Abyss, notable for its action-oriented combat system, expansive open world, and detailed character customization. Players explore the open world through dynamic combat and engage in rich economic activities and trade. It also features combat elements such as PvP battles, large-scale group battles, and castle conquests. Visually stunning, BDO offers players detailed character customization options and activities like animal breeding. Overall, it&apos;s a popular choice for those seeking an intense and in-depth gaming experience.\"}', '{\"ar\": \"To redeem the Black Desert code you purchased through LikeCard, follow these steps:1- Log in to your game account with your user email address.2- Then, go to Store  Redeem Coupon from the menu.3- Enter the coupon code sent to you by LikeCard in the appropriate field.4- Click the Redeem button and confirm the notification with the \\\"OK\\\" button.\", \"en\": \"To redeem the Black Desert code you purchased through LikeCard, follow these steps:1- Log in to your game account with your user email address.2- Then, go to Store  Redeem Coupon from the menu.3- Enter the coupon code sent to you by LikeCard in the appropriate field.4- Click the Redeem button and confirm the notification with the \\\"OK\\\" button.\"}', '{\"ar\": \"1- Products are delivered instantly as an e-pin after payment is completed.2- Digital products cannot be returned in accordance with the relevant article of the Turkish Commercial Code.\", \"en\": \"1- Products are delivered instantly as an e-pin after payment is completed.2- Digital products cannot be returned in accordance with the relevant article of the Turkish Commercial Code.\"}', NULL, '2026-04-09 08:41:54', '2026-04-06 11:06:11', '2026-04-09 08:41:54');
INSERT INTO `digital_merchants` (`id`, `merchant_id`, `company_name`, `name`, `description`, `redeem_steps`, `terms`, `parent_id`, `last_synced_at`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(365, '1783', 'like_card', '{\"ar\": \"Dragon Trail\", \"en\": \"Dragon Trail\"}', '{\"ar\": \"Dragon Trail invites you to an extraordinary game that opens the doors to a world of magic and mystery, offering a rich narrative and captivating universe. This fantastical world is filled with mysteries, thrilling adventures, and memorable characters waiting to be discovered around every corner. Players will experience a deep gameplay experience with unique content as they journey through Dragon Trail&apos;s captivating universe. In this world, the keys to success are not only strength and strategy, but also imagination and creativity. Dragon Trail promises an unforgettable gaming experience that appeals to players of all ages and backgrounds.\", \"en\": \"Dragon Trail invites you to an extraordinary game that opens the doors to a world of magic and mystery, offering a rich narrative and captivating universe. This fantastical world is filled with mysteries, thrilling adventures, and memorable characters waiting to be discovered around every corner. Players will experience a deep gameplay experience with unique content as they journey through Dragon Trail&apos;s captivating universe. In this world, the keys to success are not only strength and strategy, but also imagination and creativity. Dragon Trail promises an unforgettable gaming experience that appeals to players of all ages and backgrounds.\"}', '{\"ar\": \"To activate Dragon Trail codes you purchase through LikeCard, follow the steps below:1- Click the link below and log in to your account.https://payment.wattgaming.com/selectGoods2- After logging in to your account, select the prepaid option.3- Fill out all the required information.4- Then, select the amount of the code you purchased.5- Click the \\\"Next\\\" button.Congratulations, your Dragon Trail Diamond top-up is complete.\", \"en\": \"To activate Dragon Trail codes you purchase through LikeCard, follow the steps below:1- Click the link below and log in to your account.https://payment.wattgaming.com/selectGoods2- After logging in to your account, select the prepaid option.3- Fill out all the required information.4- Then, select the amount of the code you purchased.5- Click the \\\"Next\\\" button.Congratulations, your Dragon Trail Diamond top-up is complete.\"}', '{\"ar\": \"- Digital products cannot be returned in accordance with the relevant article of the Turkish Commercial Code.\", \"en\": \"- Digital products cannot be returned in accordance with the relevant article of the Turkish Commercial Code.\"}', NULL, '2026-04-09 08:41:54', '2026-04-06 11:06:11', '2026-04-09 08:41:54'),
(366, '1784', 'like_card', '{\"ar\": \"Kung Fu Saga\", \"en\": \"Kung Fu Saga\"}', '{\"ar\": \"Kung Fu Saga offers an immersive MMORPG (Massively Multiplayer Online Role-Playing Game) experience based on Eastern martial arts. This game creates a unique world with its rich history, cultural elements, and deep martial arts-based story. Players are immersed in the mysterious atmosphere of ancient Eastern civilizations and have the opportunity to create heroes with distinctive characteristics, equipped with various fighting styles and strategies. ByNoGame opens the doors to this unique adventure by providing all the digital codes and special inventories needed to step into the exciting world of Kung Fu Saga. The game&apos;s detailed and rich visual design makes players feel as if they&apos;re on a movie set.\", \"en\": \"Kung Fu Saga offers an immersive MMORPG (Massively Multiplayer Online Role-Playing Game) experience based on Eastern martial arts. This game creates a unique world with its rich history, cultural elements, and deep martial arts-based story. Players are immersed in the mysterious atmosphere of ancient Eastern civilizations and have the opportunity to create heroes with distinctive characteristics, equipped with various fighting styles and strategies. ByNoGame opens the doors to this unique adventure by providing all the digital codes and special inventories needed to step into the exciting world of Kung Fu Saga. The game&apos;s detailed and rich visual design makes players feel as if they&apos;re on a movie set.\"}', '{\"ar\": \"To activate the Kung Fu Saga codes you purchase through LikeCard, follow these steps:1- Click the link below and log in to your account.https://payment-unit.wattgaming.com/selectGoods2- After logging in to your account, select the prepaid option.3- Fill out all the required information.4- Then, select the amount of the code you purchased.5- Click the \\\"Next\\\" button.Congratulations, your Kung Fu Saga Diamond top-up is complete.\", \"en\": \"To activate the Kung Fu Saga codes you purchase through LikeCard, follow these steps:1- Click the link below and log in to your account.https://payment-unit.wattgaming.com/selectGoods2- After logging in to your account, select the prepaid option.3- Fill out all the required information.4- Then, select the amount of the code you purchased.5- Click the \\\"Next\\\" button.Congratulations, your Kung Fu Saga Diamond top-up is complete.\"}', '{\"ar\": \"- Digital products cannot be returned in accordance with the relevant article of the Turkish Commercial Code.\", \"en\": \"- Digital products cannot be returned in accordance with the relevant article of the Turkish Commercial Code.\"}', NULL, '2026-04-09 08:41:54', '2026-04-06 11:06:11', '2026-04-09 08:41:54'),
(367, '1785', 'like_card', '{\"ar\": \"Legend Online Reborn\", \"en\": \"Legend Online Reborn\"}', '{\"ar\": \"Legend Online Reborn is a browser-based MMORPG. It&apos;s a remake of Legend Online, featuring enhanced graphics, an in-depth combat system, and strategic options. Develop your character and face challenging enemies with auto-battlers and robust customization options. It delivers a constantly fresh experience with new levels and dynamic events. Its user-friendly interface and modern visuals appeal to both new and experienced players. Discover Legend Online Reborn for an epic adventure!\", \"en\": \"Legend Online Reborn is a browser-based MMORPG. It&apos;s a remake of Legend Online, featuring enhanced graphics, an in-depth combat system, and strategic options. Develop your character and face challenging enemies with auto-battlers and robust customization options. It delivers a constantly fresh experience with new levels and dynamic events. Its user-friendly interface and modern visuals appeal to both new and experienced players. Discover Legend Online Reborn for an epic adventure!\"}', '{\"ar\": \"To activate the Legend Online Reborn codes you purchase through LikeCard, follow these steps:<br>1- Go to https://lotr.creaction-network.com2- Click \\\"Payment. 3- Click the E-pin tab in your payment method. Select \\\"Oasis E-pin\\\" from the payment method and select the amount of diamonds you purchased from our site. After clicking the \\\"Buy\\\" button, enter the E-pin code on the screen that appears.\", \"en\": \"To activate the Legend Online Reborn codes you purchase through LikeCard, follow these steps:<br>1- Go to https://lotr.creaction-network.com2- Click \\\"Payment. 3- Click the E-pin tab in your payment method. Select \\\"Oasis E-pin\\\" from the payment method and select the amount of diamonds you purchased from our site. After clicking the \\\"Buy\\\" button, enter the E-pin code on the screen that appears.\"}', '{\"ar\": \"1- Products are delivered instantly as an e-pin after payment is completed.2- Digital products cannot be returned in accordance with the relevant article of the Turkish Commercial Code.\", \"en\": \"1- Products are delivered instantly as an e-pin after payment is completed.2- Digital products cannot be returned in accordance with the relevant article of the Turkish Commercial Code.\"}', NULL, '2026-04-09 08:41:54', '2026-04-06 11:06:11', '2026-04-09 08:41:54'),
(368, '1462', 'like_card', '{\"ar\": \"Biletinial\", \"en\": \"Biletinial\"}', '{\"ar\": \"Biletinial is a ticketing company that provides solutions and connects consumers with cinema, theater, music, sports, and many other events.Biletinial bipuan is Biletinial&apos;s first and only event ticket earning program.The Bipuan platform offers access to thousands of different events nationwide, including cinema, theater, sports, and concerts.\", \"en\": \"Biletinial is a ticketing company that provides solutions and connects consumers with cinema, theater, music, sports, and many other events.Biletinial bipuan is Biletinial&apos;s first and only event ticket earning program.The Bipuan platform offers access to thousands of different events nationwide, including cinema, theater, sports, and concerts.\"}', '{\"ar\": \"To activate the Biletinial Bipuan codes you purchase through LikeCard, follow the steps below:1) Go to https://biletinial.com/webLogin/mywallet.2) Click the \\\"Load Bipuan with Coupon\\\" button.3) Enter the Biletinial Bipuan Code you purchased from LikeCard in the appropriate field and click the \\\"Load\\\" button.\", \"en\": \"To activate the Biletinial Bipuan codes you purchase through LikeCard, follow the steps below:1) Go to https://biletinial.com/webLogin/mywallet.2) Click the \\\"Load Bipuan with Coupon\\\" button.3) Enter the Biletinial Bipuan Code you purchased from LikeCard in the appropriate field and click the \\\"Load\\\" button.\"}', '{\"ar\": \"1- Bipoints can be used at most events on the Biletinial platform.2- Existing Bipoints are valid for one year.3- Digital products cannot be returned, in accordance with the relevant article of the Turkish Commercial Code.\", \"en\": \"1- Bipoints can be used at most events on the Biletinial platform.2- Existing Bipoints are valid for one year.3- Digital products cannot be returned, in accordance with the relevant article of the Turkish Commercial Code.\"}', NULL, '2026-04-09 08:41:54', '2026-04-06 11:06:11', '2026-04-09 08:41:54'),
(369, '1465', 'like_card', '{\"ar\": \"Theather Clix\", \"en\": \"Theather Clix\"}', '{\"ar\": \"Theatre Clix is ​​a digital theatre platform where you can watch local and international plays for adults and children, anytime, anywhere, on any internet-connected smart device.You can watch on your Smart TV, Apple TV, tablet, mobile phone, PC, laptop, consoles, and any other internet-connected smart device.Theatre Clix subscriptions include international and domestic plays for adults and/or children, musicals, and sand art performances.Theatre Clix subscriptions also offer discounts on theatre tickets.\", \"en\": \"Theatre Clix is ​​a digital theatre platform where you can watch local and international plays for adults and children, anytime, anywhere, on any internet-connected smart device.You can watch on your Smart TV, Apple TV, tablet, mobile phone, PC, laptop, consoles, and any other internet-connected smart device.Theatre Clix subscriptions include international and domestic plays for adults and/or children, musicals, and sand art performances.Theatre Clix subscriptions also offer discounts on theatre tickets.\"}', '{\"ar\": \"To activate the Theater Clix subscription codes you purchase through LikeCard, follow the steps below:1) Go to www.TheatreClix.com and click the \\\"Use Code\\\" button.2) Select the subscription you purchased.3) Complete the process by entering your code in the \\\"Campaign Code\\\" section on the Cart or Checkout page.4) The discount amount will be automatically refunded to your card after your payment.\", \"en\": \"To activate the Theater Clix subscription codes you purchase through LikeCard, follow the steps below:1) Go to www.TheatreClix.com and click the \\\"Use Code\\\" button.2) Select the subscription you purchased.3) Complete the process by entering your code in the \\\"Campaign Code\\\" section on the Cart or Checkout page.4) The discount amount will be automatically refunded to your card after your payment.\"}', '{\"ar\": \"In accordance with the relevant article of the Turkish Commercial Code, digital products cannot be returned.\", \"en\": \"In accordance with the relevant article of the Turkish Commercial Code, digital products cannot be returned.\"}', NULL, '2026-04-09 08:41:54', '2026-04-06 11:06:11', '2026-04-09 08:41:54'),
(370, '1355', 'like_card', '{\"ar\": \"TV+ - TR\", \"en\": \"TV+ - TR\"}', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2026-04-09 08:41:54', '2026-04-06 11:06:11', '2026-04-09 08:41:54'),
(371, '1357', 'like_card', '{\"ar\": \"EyesPro - TR\", \"en\": \"EyesPro - TR\"}', '{\"ar\": \"- EyesPro automatically monitors the distance between your eyes and your smartphone and warns you to move the screen away from your eyes if the distance is closer than you set.- You can adjust the screen distance yourself for eye protection, but experts recommend 30 cm.- A blue light filter reduces the negative effects of light emitted from a smartphone or tablet screen.- The app allows you to set a timer so your phone&apos;s screen color automatically changes to a warmer color during setup.You can also adjust the level of color temperature enhancement or reduction.\", \"en\": \"- EyesPro automatically monitors the distance between your eyes and your smartphone and warns you to move the screen away from your eyes if the distance is closer than you set.- You can adjust the screen distance yourself for eye protection, but experts recommend 30 cm.- A blue light filter reduces the negative effects of light emitted from a smartphone or tablet screen.- The app allows you to set a timer so your phone&apos;s screen color automatically changes to a warmer color during setup.You can also adjust the level of color temperature enhancement or reduction.\"}', '{\"ar\": \"To activate the EyesPro codes you purchase through LikeCard, follow the steps below:1) Download the EyesPro app to your mobile phone and register.2) Click the card icon on the login screen, which displays the payment options.3) Click the LICENSE CODE button. Enter the EyesPro Package code you purchased from LikeCard.4) Click the &apos;SEND&apos; button.\", \"en\": \"To activate the EyesPro codes you purchase through LikeCard, follow the steps below:1) Download the EyesPro app to your mobile phone and register.2) Click the card icon on the login screen, which displays the payment options.3) Click the LICENSE CODE button. Enter the EyesPro Package code you purchased from LikeCard.4) Click the &apos;SEND&apos; button.\"}', '{\"ar\": \"- Digital products cannot be returned in accordance with the relevant article of the Turkish Commercial Code.\", \"en\": \"- Digital products cannot be returned in accordance with the relevant article of the Turkish Commercial Code.\"}', NULL, '2026-04-09 08:41:54', '2026-04-06 11:06:11', '2026-04-09 08:41:54'),
(372, '1697', 'like_card', '{\"ar\": \"Ace Racer\", \"en\": \"Ace Racer\"}', '{\"ar\": \"Ace Racer is a racing mobile game introducing innovative vehicles with ultimate skills. Experience various actual cars from legendary vehicle manufacturers like Porsche and Nissan, along with our own custom creations.\", \"en\": \"Ace Racer is a racing mobile game introducing innovative vehicles with ultimate skills. Experience various actual cars from legendary vehicle manufacturers like Porsche and Nissan, along with our own custom creations.\"}', '{\"ar\": \"To activate your Gift Card Voucher please follow the below steps:1- Go to https://pay.neteasegames.com/ 2-  Select your game server3-  Enter your ID4-  Enter the code and select the “Continue” button5-  Enter your serial number (Redeem code)6-  Enter the “Activate” button\", \"en\": \"To activate your Gift Card Voucher please follow the below steps:1- Go to https://pay.neteasegames.com/ 2-  Select your game server3-  Enter your ID4-  Enter the code and select the “Continue” button5-  Enter your serial number (Redeem code)6-  Enter the “Activate” button\"}', '{\"ar\": \"1) Valid for 10 years. 2) Once purchased, cannot be returned or refunded\", \"en\": \"1) Valid for 10 years. 2) Once purchased, cannot be returned or refunded\"}', NULL, '2026-04-09 08:41:54', '2026-04-06 11:06:11', '2026-04-09 08:41:54'),
(373, '1698', 'like_card', '{\"ar\": \"Blood Strike MENA\", \"en\": \"Blood Strike MENA\"}', '{\"ar\": \"Blood Strike is a fast-paced battle royale FPS game where the action never stops. Players choose operators with unique abilities and dive into intense combat. With high mobility, powerful weapons, and strategic gameplay, every moment is packed with adrenaline. The goal: be the last one standing!\", \"en\": \"Blood Strike is a fast-paced battle royale FPS game where the action never stops. Players choose operators with unique abilities and dive into intense combat. With high mobility, powerful weapons, and strategic gameplay, every moment is packed with adrenaline. The goal: be the last one standing!\"}', '{\"ar\": \"To activate your Gift Card Voucher please follow the below steps:• Go to https://pay.neteasegames.com/ • Select your game server• Enter your ID• Enter the code and select the “Continue” button• Enter your serial number (Redeem code)• Enter the “Activate” button\", \"en\": \"To activate your Gift Card Voucher please follow the below steps:• Go to https://pay.neteasegames.com/ • Select your game server• Enter your ID• Enter the code and select the “Continue” button• Enter your serial number (Redeem code)• Enter the “Activate” button\"}', '{\"ar\": \"1-  Valid for 10 years. 2-  Once purchased, cannot be returned or refunded.\", \"en\": \"1-  Valid for 10 years. 2-  Once purchased, cannot be returned or refunded.\"}', NULL, '2026-04-09 08:41:54', '2026-04-06 11:06:11', '2026-04-09 08:41:54'),
(374, '1699', 'like_card', '{\"ar\": \"Blood Strike\", \"en\": \"Blood Strike\"}', '{\"ar\": \"Blood Strike is a fast-paced, free-to-play mobile battle royale game with smooth controls and high-definition visuals, even on lower-end devices. It emphasizes tactical combat\", \"en\": \"Blood Strike is a fast-paced, free-to-play mobile battle royale game with smooth controls and high-definition visuals, even on lower-end devices. It emphasizes tactical combat\"}', '{\"ar\": \"To activate your Gift Card Voucher please follow the below steps:• Go to https://pay.neteasegames.com/ • Select your game server• Enter your ID• Enter the code and select the “Continue” button• Enter your serial number (Redeem code)• Enter the “Activate” button\", \"en\": \"To activate your Gift Card Voucher please follow the below steps:• Go to https://pay.neteasegames.com/ • Select your game server• Enter your ID• Enter the code and select the “Continue” button• Enter your serial number (Redeem code)• Enter the “Activate” button\"}', '{\"ar\": \"1-  Valid for 10 years. 2-  Once purchased, cannot be returned or refunded.\", \"en\": \"1-  Valid for 10 years. 2-  Once purchased, cannot be returned or refunded.\"}', NULL, '2026-04-09 08:41:54', '2026-04-06 11:06:11', '2026-04-09 08:41:54'),
(375, '1700', 'like_card', '{\"ar\": \"Dead by Daylight Mobile\", \"en\": \"Dead by Daylight Mobile\"}', '{\"ar\": \"Dead by Daylight Mobile is an asymmetric multiplayer horror game. One player controls a ruthless killer, while four others play as survivors trying to escape. Strategy, stealth, and teamwork are key to survival! With its intense atmosphere and licensed horror characters, it&apos;s a must-play experience for horror fans.\", \"en\": \"Dead by Daylight Mobile is an asymmetric multiplayer horror game. One player controls a ruthless killer, while four others play as survivors trying to escape. Strategy, stealth, and teamwork are key to survival! With its intense atmosphere and licensed horror characters, it&apos;s a must-play experience for horror fans.\"}', '{\"ar\": \"To activate your Gift Card Voucher please follow the below steps:• Go to https://pay.neteasegames.com/ • Select your game server• Enter your ID• Enter the code and select the “Continue” button• Enter your serial number (Redeem code)• Enter the “Activate” button\", \"en\": \"To activate your Gift Card Voucher please follow the below steps:• Go to https://pay.neteasegames.com/ • Select your game server• Enter your ID• Enter the code and select the “Continue” button• Enter your serial number (Redeem code)• Enter the “Activate” button\"}', '{\"ar\": \"1- Valid for 10 years. 2- Once purchased, cannot be returned or refunded\", \"en\": \"1- Valid for 10 years. 2- Once purchased, cannot be returned or refunded\"}', NULL, '2026-04-09 08:41:54', '2026-04-06 11:06:11', '2026-04-09 08:41:54'),
(376, '1701', 'like_card', '{\"ar\": \"Eggy Party\", \"en\": \"Eggy Party\"}', '{\"ar\": \"a free-to-play, party royale game where players compete in various mini-games, obstacle courses, and arenas, often resembling a casual version of Fall Guys.\", \"en\": \"a free-to-play, party royale game where players compete in various mini-games, obstacle courses, and arenas, often resembling a casual version of Fall Guys.\"}', '{\"ar\": \"To activate your Gift Card Voucher please follow the below steps:• Go to https://pay.neteasegames.com/ • Select your game server• Enter your ID• Enter the code and select the “Continue” button• Enter your serial number (Redeem code)• Enter the “Activate” button\", \"en\": \"To activate your Gift Card Voucher please follow the below steps:• Go to https://pay.neteasegames.com/ • Select your game server• Enter your ID• Enter the code and select the “Continue” button• Enter your serial number (Redeem code)• Enter the “Activate” button\"}', '{\"ar\": \"1) Valid for 10 years. 2) Once purchased, cannot be returned or refunded\", \"en\": \"1) Valid for 10 years. 2) Once purchased, cannot be returned or refunded\"}', NULL, '2026-04-09 08:41:54', '2026-04-06 11:06:11', '2026-04-09 08:41:54'),
(377, '1702', 'like_card', '{\"ar\": \"EVE Echoes\", \"en\": \"EVE Echoes\"}', '{\"ar\": \"EVE Echoes is a deep, strategy-rich MMORPG set in a vast space universe. In this game, players control their own spaceships, engage in trading, and participate in epic battles. AUR codes in EVE Echoes allow you to purchase various in-game advantages, ships, equipment, and the premium currency AUR. Easily buy AUR codes via Liderepin and take your space adventures to the next level!\", \"en\": \"EVE Echoes is a deep, strategy-rich MMORPG set in a vast space universe. In this game, players control their own spaceships, engage in trading, and participate in epic battles. AUR codes in EVE Echoes allow you to purchase various in-game advantages, ships, equipment, and the premium currency AUR. Easily buy AUR codes via Liderepin and take your space adventures to the next level!\"}', '{\"ar\": \"To activate your Gift Card Voucher please follow the below steps:• Go to https://pay.neteasegames.com/ • Select your game server• Enter your ID• Enter the code and select the “Continue” button• Enter your serial number (Redeem code)• Enter the “Activate” button\", \"en\": \"To activate your Gift Card Voucher please follow the below steps:• Go to https://pay.neteasegames.com/ • Select your game server• Enter your ID• Enter the code and select the “Continue” button• Enter your serial number (Redeem code)• Enter the “Activate” button\"}', '{\"ar\": \"1-  Valid for 10 years. 2-  Once purchased, cannot be returned or refunded. \", \"en\": \"1-  Valid for 10 years. 2-  Once purchased, cannot be returned or refunded. \"}', NULL, '2026-04-09 08:41:54', '2026-04-06 11:06:11', '2026-04-09 08:41:54'),
(378, '1703', 'like_card', '{\"ar\": \"Harry Potter Magic Awakened\", \"en\": \"Harry Potter Magic Awakened\"}', '{\"ar\": \"a mobile game combining RPG and card-based combat within the Harry Potter universe. Set ten years after the Battle of Hogwarts, players attend Hogwarts as new students, customize their characters, learn spells, and duel other players.\", \"en\": \"a mobile game combining RPG and card-based combat within the Harry Potter universe. Set ten years after the Battle of Hogwarts, players attend Hogwarts as new students, customize their characters, learn spells, and duel other players.\"}', '{\"ar\": \"To activate your Gift Card Voucher please follow the below steps:1-  Go to https://pay.neteasegames.com/ 2-  Select your game server3-  Enter your ID4-  Enter the code and select the “Continue” button5-  Enter your serial number (Redeem code)6- Enter the “Activate” button\", \"en\": \"To activate your Gift Card Voucher please follow the below steps:1-  Go to https://pay.neteasegames.com/ 2-  Select your game server3-  Enter your ID4-  Enter the code and select the “Continue” button5-  Enter your serial number (Redeem code)6- Enter the “Activate” button\"}', '{\"ar\": \"1-  Valid for 10 years. 2-  Once purchased, cannot be returned or refunded\", \"en\": \"1-  Valid for 10 years. 2-  Once purchased, cannot be returned or refunded\"}', NULL, '2026-04-09 08:41:54', '2026-04-06 11:06:11', '2026-04-09 08:41:54'),
(379, '1704', 'like_card', '{\"ar\": \"The Lord of the rings Rise to War\", \"en\": \"The Lord of the rings Rise to War\"}', '{\"ar\": \"Based on the Oscar-winning The Lord of the Rings film, The Lord of the Rings: Rise to War – Age of Wars was released on September 23, 2021, by NetEase Games and Warner Bros Interactive. This mobile strategy and war game, which includes Turkish language support, lets you command your army in the Middle-earth war alongside iconic heroes like Frodo, Aragorn, Gandalf, and others.\", \"en\": \"Based on the Oscar-winning The Lord of the Rings film, The Lord of the Rings: Rise to War – Age of Wars was released on September 23, 2021, by NetEase Games and Warner Bros Interactive. This mobile strategy and war game, which includes Turkish language support, lets you command your army in the Middle-earth war alongside iconic heroes like Frodo, Aragorn, Gandalf, and others.\"}', '{\"ar\": \"To activate your Gift Card Voucher please follow the below steps:• Go to https://pay.neteasegames.com/ • Select your game server• Enter your ID• Enter the code and select the “Continue” button• Enter your serial number (Redeem code)• Enter the “Activate” button\", \"en\": \"To activate your Gift Card Voucher please follow the below steps:• Go to https://pay.neteasegames.com/ • Select your game server• Enter your ID• Enter the code and select the “Continue” button• Enter your serial number (Redeem code)• Enter the “Activate” button\"}', '{\"ar\": \"1) Valid for 10 years. 2) Once purchased, cannot be returned or refunded\", \"en\": \"1) Valid for 10 years. 2) Once purchased, cannot be returned or refunded\"}', NULL, '2026-04-09 08:41:54', '2026-04-06 11:06:11', '2026-04-09 08:41:54'),
(380, '1707', 'like_card', '{\"ar\": \"Hediyen Kart\", \"en\": \"Hediyen Kart\"}', '{\"ar\": \"Hediyen Kart (Gift Card) is a gift card system used in Türkiye.This card can be purchased digitally or physically and can be used at a variety of businesses, including stores, restaurants, and e-commerce sites.When given as a gift, Hediyen Kart offers the recipient the freedom to choose the product or service they desire.Users can load a certain amount of money onto their card and spend it at places that accept the card.It is popular as both a personal gift and a corporate gift.\", \"en\": \"Hediyen Kart (Gift Card) is a gift card system used in Türkiye.This card can be purchased digitally or physically and can be used at a variety of businesses, including stores, restaurants, and e-commerce sites.When given as a gift, Hediyen Kart offers the recipient the freedom to choose the product or service they desire.Users can load a certain amount of money onto their card and spend it at places that accept the card.It is popular as both a personal gift and a corporate gift.\"}', '{\"ar\": \"To activate the Hediyen Card codes you purchase through LikeCard, follow the steps below:To use the product code:1. Go to hediyenkart.com, register to save your Hediyen Card balance to your account, and verify your account with the link sent to your email address.2. Enter your 14-digit E-PIN Hediyen Card code on the website to top up your Hediyen Card balance.3. To redeem your balance, choose from a wide variety of brands and use the coupon code you receive by shopping at the brand&apos;s website or in stores of your choosing.\", \"en\": \"To activate the Hediyen Card codes you purchase through LikeCard, follow the steps below:To use the product code:1. Go to hediyenkart.com, register to save your Hediyen Card balance to your account, and verify your account with the link sent to your email address.2. Enter your 14-digit E-PIN Hediyen Card code on the website to top up your Hediyen Card balance.3. To redeem your balance, choose from a wide variety of brands and use the coupon code you receive by shopping at the brand&apos;s website or in stores of your choosing.\"}', '{\"ar\": \"1- A digital gift code consists of a 14-digit code.2- The digital gift code expires 24 months from the date you receive the code.3- You can add the amount in your digital gift code to your account by visiting www.hediyenkart.com. You can then use your balance all at once or in installments by purchasing gift certificates from your chosen brand.4- If you don&apos;t have an account on hediyenkart.com, you can easily create an account free of charge and step into the vibrant world of Hediyen Kart.5- Digital gift certificates cannot be exchanged for cash, and unused balances cannot be refunded.6- If a gift certificate code is lost, a new one cannot be generated, balances cannot be transferred to a different card/check, or a replacement gift certificate cannot be issued. 7- The responsibility for the lost code rests with the gift certificate holder.8- In accordance with the relevant article of the Turkish Commercial Code, returns cannot be made for digital products.\", \"en\": \"1- A digital gift code consists of a 14-digit code.2- The digital gift code expires 24 months from the date you receive the code.3- You can add the amount in your digital gift code to your account by visiting www.hediyenkart.com. You can then use your balance all at once or in installments by purchasing gift certificates from your chosen brand.4- If you don&apos;t have an account on hediyenkart.com, you can easily create an account free of charge and step into the vibrant world of Hediyen Kart.5- Digital gift certificates cannot be exchanged for cash, and unused balances cannot be refunded.6- If a gift certificate code is lost, a new one cannot be generated, balances cannot be transferred to a different card/check, or a replacement gift certificate cannot be issued. 7- The responsibility for the lost code rests with the gift certificate holder.8- In accordance with the relevant article of the Turkish Commercial Code, returns cannot be made for digital products.\"}', NULL, '2026-04-09 08:41:54', '2026-04-06 11:06:11', '2026-04-09 08:41:54'),
(381, '1706', 'like_card', '{\"ar\": \"Kobo\", \"en\": \"Kobo\"}', '{\"ar\": \"Do you listen to audiobooks? Or are you an e-book enthusiast? A Kobo gift card gives you access to millions of captivating stories! From bestsellers to hidden gems, classics to new releases, the Kobo online store has every e-book you&apos;re looking for. All you need is a Kobo gift card from LikeCard. Simply select your Kobo gift card amount, enter your email address, and pay securely with your credit card. You&apos;ll receive your code by email within minutes.Find the Kobo product you&apos;re looking for and download it to your Kobo eReader or the free Kobo app. Adventure awaits!\", \"en\": \"Do you listen to audiobooks? Or are you an e-book enthusiast? A Kobo gift card gives you access to millions of captivating stories! From bestsellers to hidden gems, classics to new releases, the Kobo online store has every e-book you&apos;re looking for. All you need is a Kobo gift card from LikeCard. Simply select your Kobo gift card amount, enter your email address, and pay securely with your credit card. You&apos;ll receive your code by email within minutes.Find the Kobo product you&apos;re looking for and download it to your Kobo eReader or the free Kobo app. Adventure awaits!\"}', '{\"ar\": \"To activate Kobo gift cards you purchase through LikeCard, follow these steps:1-  Log in or create a Kobo account.2-  Go to the eBook you want to purchase and add it to your shopping cart.3-  Check Yes next to the question, \\\"Do you have a gift card?\\\"4-  Enter your gift card code in the box below and click Apply to confirm.\", \"en\": \"To activate Kobo gift cards you purchase through LikeCard, follow these steps:1-  Log in or create a Kobo account.2-  Go to the eBook you want to purchase and add it to your shopping cart.3-  Check Yes next to the question, \\\"Do you have a gift card?\\\"4-  Enter your gift card code in the box below and click Apply to confirm.\"}', '{\"ar\": \"1- The Kobo online store offers countless audiobooks and e-books you can read on your Kobo eReader. Use or send a Kobo gift card to purchase e-books and audiobooks here.2- You must have a Kobo account to redeem your code. Log in or create one here.3- The Kobo gift card has no expiration date!4- Digital products cannot be returned, as per the relevant article of the Turkish Commercial Code.\", \"en\": \"1- The Kobo online store offers countless audiobooks and e-books you can read on your Kobo eReader. Use or send a Kobo gift card to purchase e-books and audiobooks here.2- You must have a Kobo account to redeem your code. Log in or create one here.3- The Kobo gift card has no expiration date!4- Digital products cannot be returned, as per the relevant article of the Turkish Commercial Code.\"}', NULL, '2026-04-09 08:41:54', '2026-04-06 11:06:11', '2026-04-09 08:41:54'),
(382, '2003', 'like_card', '{\"ar\": \"2XKO (PC and Console)\", \"en\": \"2XKO (PC and Console)\"}', '{\"ar\": \"2XKO is a 2v2 fighting game where good teamwork can make the difference between victory and defeat. Master a variety of unique tag and assist mechanics to outplay the enemy duo and secure your spot at the top.\", \"en\": \"2XKO is a 2v2 fighting game where good teamwork can make the difference between victory and defeat. Master a variety of unique tag and assist mechanics to outplay the enemy duo and secure your spot at the top.\"}', '{\"ar\": \"How to redeem 2XKO cards:1- Log into the 2XKO game client.2- Click on the 2XKO icon located to the right of the Store tab.3- Select Prepaid Cards & Codes.4- Input the code provided for your card.5- Press Submit.6- Enjoy your 2XKO Points!\\\\n7- Available to play on PC and Console.\\\\nTo redeem your Riot Access code across all platforms, please visit:\\\\n https://shop.riotgames.com/redeem \", \"en\": \"How to redeem 2XKO cards:1- Log into the 2XKO game client.2- Click on the 2XKO icon located to the right of the Store tab.3- Select Prepaid Cards & Codes.4- Input the code provided for your card.5- Press Submit.6- Enjoy your 2XKO Points!\\\\n7- Available to play on PC and Console.\\\\nTo redeem your Riot Access code across all platforms, please visit:\\\\n https://shop.riotgames.com/redeem \"}', '{\"ar\": \"You can only use the e-voucher / gift card for one time.\", \"en\": \"You can only use the e-voucher / gift card for one time.\"}', NULL, '2026-04-09 08:41:54', '2026-04-06 11:06:11', '2026-04-09 08:41:54'),
(383, '3084', 'like_card', '{\"ar\": \"Whiteout Survival\", \"en\": \"Whiteout Survival\"}', '{\"ar\": \"Whiteout Survival is a strategic survival game set in the midst of a devastating ice catastrophe. The world has plunged into a deep freeze, and the collapse of civilization has pushed humanity to the brink of extinction.As the leader of the last remaining city, you must guide your people through relentless snowstorms, deadly beasts, and ruthless bandits. Build shelters, manage resources, and make critical decisions to ensure humanity’s survival in this frozen wasteland.Do you have what it takes to lead the survivors and rebuild civilization from the ice?\", \"en\": \"Whiteout Survival is a strategic survival game set in the midst of a devastating ice catastrophe. The world has plunged into a deep freeze, and the collapse of civilization has pushed humanity to the brink of extinction.As the leader of the last remaining city, you must guide your people through relentless snowstorms, deadly beasts, and ruthless bandits. Build shelters, manage resources, and make critical decisions to ensure humanity’s survival in this frozen wasteland.Do you have what it takes to lead the survivors and rebuild civilization from the ice?\"}', '{\"ar\": \"1- Select the Whiteout Survival Frost Star package you wish to purchase.2- Enter your Whiteout Survival Frost Star Player ID.3- Choose your preferred payment method (such as bank transfer, card, or e-wallet).4- Complete the purchase process.5- Once the payment is successfully completed, your items will be delivered directly to your Whiteout Survival Frost Star account.\", \"en\": \"1- Select the Whiteout Survival Frost Star package you wish to purchase.2- Enter your Whiteout Survival Frost Star Player ID.3- Choose your preferred payment method (such as bank transfer, card, or e-wallet).4- Complete the purchase process.5- Once the payment is successfully completed, your items will be delivered directly to your Whiteout Survival Frost Star account.\"}', NULL, NULL, '2026-04-09 08:41:54', '2026-04-06 11:06:11', '2026-04-09 08:41:54'),
(384, '2026', 'like_card', '{\"ar\": \"Call Of Duty Mobile - KSA\", \"en\": \"Call Of Duty Mobile - KSA\"}', '{\"ar\": \"Call of Duty: Mobile, or CODM for short, is an adrenaline rush. CODM is a free-to-play mobile game that brings the famous \\\"Call of Duty\\\" PC game franchise to smartphones and tablets. CODM was launched in 2019 by Activision.There are plenty of reasons as to why this mobile game is so popular. You won’t ever get bored of various action-packed gameplay modes, like team-based multiplayer, battle royale, and playing in iconic maps from other Call of Duty games.Also, players can customize their airdropped weapon supplies, access various types of weapons and shoot their way to the top spot at events and challenges to earn rewards.Call of Duty: Mobile delivers an immersive and action-packed gaming experience like no other for fans of Call of Duty who are on the move.\", \"en\": \"Call of Duty: Mobile, or CODM for short, is an adrenaline rush. CODM is a free-to-play mobile game that brings the famous \\\"Call of Duty\\\" PC game franchise to smartphones and tablets. CODM was launched in 2019 by Activision.There are plenty of reasons as to why this mobile game is so popular. You won’t ever get bored of various action-packed gameplay modes, like team-based multiplayer, battle royale, and playing in iconic maps from other Call of Duty games.Also, players can customize their airdropped weapon supplies, access various types of weapons and shoot their way to the top spot at events and challenges to earn rewards.Call of Duty: Mobile delivers an immersive and action-packed gaming experience like no other for fans of Call of Duty who are on the move.\"}', '{\"ar\": \"To find your PlayerID:\\\\n1- Log in to your CODM profile and enter the game lobby.\\\\n2- Click on the \\\"Settings\\\" button at the top right.\\\\n3- In \\\"Settings\\\", click on the \\\"LEGAL AND PRIVACY\\\" tab and you will find your PlayerID.\", \"en\": \"To find your PlayerID:\\\\n1- Log in to your CODM profile and enter the game lobby.\\\\n2- Click on the \\\"Settings\\\" button at the top right.\\\\n3- In \\\"Settings\\\", click on the \\\"LEGAL AND PRIVACY\\\" tab and you will find your PlayerID.\"}', '{\"ar\": \"PLEASE ENSURE THAT YOU HAVE THE LATEST VERSION OF CALL OF DUTY: MOBILE BEFORE PURCHASING.\", \"en\": \"PLEASE ENSURE THAT YOU HAVE THE LATEST VERSION OF CALL OF DUTY: MOBILE BEFORE PURCHASING.\"}', NULL, '2026-04-09 08:41:54', '2026-04-06 11:06:11', '2026-04-09 08:41:54'),
(385, '2027', 'like_card', '{\"ar\": \"Call Of Duty Mobile - UAE\", \"en\": \"Call Of Duty Mobile - UAE\"}', '{\"ar\": \"Call of Duty: Mobile, or CODM for short, is an adrenaline rush. CODM is a free-to-play mobile game that brings the famous \\\"Call of Duty\\\" PC game franchise to smartphones and tablets. CODM was launched in 2019 by Activision.There are plenty of reasons as to why this mobile game is so popular. You won’t ever get bored of various action-packed gameplay modes, like team-based multiplayer, battle royale, and playing in iconic maps from other Call of Duty games.Also, players can customize their airdropped weapon supplies, access various types of weapons and shoot their way to the top spot at events and challenges to earn rewards.Call of Duty: Mobile delivers an immersive and action-packed gaming experience like no other for fans of Call of Duty who are on the move.\", \"en\": \"Call of Duty: Mobile, or CODM for short, is an adrenaline rush. CODM is a free-to-play mobile game that brings the famous \\\"Call of Duty\\\" PC game franchise to smartphones and tablets. CODM was launched in 2019 by Activision.There are plenty of reasons as to why this mobile game is so popular. You won’t ever get bored of various action-packed gameplay modes, like team-based multiplayer, battle royale, and playing in iconic maps from other Call of Duty games.Also, players can customize their airdropped weapon supplies, access various types of weapons and shoot their way to the top spot at events and challenges to earn rewards.Call of Duty: Mobile delivers an immersive and action-packed gaming experience like no other for fans of Call of Duty who are on the move.\"}', '{\"ar\": \"To find your PlayerID:\\\\n1- Log in to your CODM profile and enter the game lobby.\\\\n2- Click on the \\\"Settings\\\" button at the top right.\\\\n3- In \\\"Settings\\\", click on the \\\"LEGAL AND PRIVACY\\\" tab and you will find your PlayerID.\", \"en\": \"To find your PlayerID:\\\\n1- Log in to your CODM profile and enter the game lobby.\\\\n2- Click on the \\\"Settings\\\" button at the top right.\\\\n3- In \\\"Settings\\\", click on the \\\"LEGAL AND PRIVACY\\\" tab and you will find your PlayerID.\"}', '{\"ar\": \"PLEASE ENSURE THAT YOU HAVE THE LATEST VERSION OF CALL OF DUTY: MOBILE BEFORE PURCHASING.\", \"en\": \"PLEASE ENSURE THAT YOU HAVE THE LATEST VERSION OF CALL OF DUTY: MOBILE BEFORE PURCHASING.\"}', NULL, '2026-04-09 08:41:54', '2026-04-06 11:06:11', '2026-04-09 08:41:54'),
