(388, '64', 'like_card', '{\"ar\": \"USA Google Play\", \"en\": \"USA Google Play\"}', '{\"ar\": \"Get Google Play cards and enjoy thousands of books, songs, movies, applications, stores and much more on the Google Play Store\", \"en\": \"Get Google Play cards and enjoy thousands of books, songs, movies, applications, stores and much more on the Google Play Store\"}', '{\"ar\": \"How to redeem Google Play cards:\\\\nThrough the app:\\\\n1- Go to the Google Play Store and click on the side menu button.\\\\n2- Enter the payment methods.\\\\n3- Click on Use Code.\\\\n4- Enter the card code that you got.\\\\n5- Click on redeem value.\\\\nthrough the browser:\\\\n1- Enter the link https://play.google.com/store/games?code\\\\n2- Enter the card code that you got.\\\\n3- Click on Redeem.\\\\nATTENTION: This card is intended exclusively for American accounts, and therefore your account must be American and registered with a real American number and address so that you do not encounter any problem when trying to charge or use the card.\\\\n\", \"en\": \"How to redeem Google Play cards:\\\\nThrough the app:\\\\n1- Go to the Google Play Store and click on the side menu button.\\\\n2- Enter the payment methods.\\\\n3- Click on Use Code.\\\\n4- Enter the card code that you got.\\\\n5- Click on redeem value.\\\\nthrough the browser:\\\\n1- Enter the link https://play.google.com/store/games?code\\\\n2- Enter the card code that you got.\\\\n3- Click on Redeem.\\\\nATTENTION: This card is intended exclusively for American accounts, and therefore your account must be American and registered with a real American number and address so that you do not encounter any problem when trying to charge or use the card.\\\\n\"}', '{\"ar\": \"1- Please visit: terms for complete terms.2- The user must be: (a) 13 years of age or older (provided that any user between the ages of 13 and 21 years of age must have their guardian&apos;s consent as required under applicable law);3- (b) resides in the United States of America.4-A Google Payments account and internet calls are required.5- Redeemed balance is maintained by Google Arizona LLC’s (“GAZ”) affiliate, Google Payment Corp. (“GPC”), in your Google Payments account. The card can be used to purchase eligible goods only and cannot be used to purchase Google Play devices and certain subscriptions.6- Other restrictions may apply. There are no fees or expiry dates.7- Except as required by law, the card is non-refundable or rechargeable or refundable for cash or exchangeable or cannot be merged with other Google Payments accounts in Google Play, in addition, cannot be resold or exchanged or transferred.8- The user is responsible for the loss of the card.9- For assistance or to check your card balance on Google Play Gift Code card balance, please visit: support. Google Play Gift Code card is issued by Google Arizona LLC.\", \"en\": \"1- Please visit: terms for complete terms.2- The user must be: (a) 13 years of age or older (provided that any user between the ages of 13 and 21 years of age must have their guardian&apos;s consent as required under applicable law);3- (b) resides in the United States of America.4-A Google Payments account and internet calls are required.5- Redeemed balance is maintained by Google Arizona LLC’s (“GAZ”) affiliate, Google Payment Corp. (“GPC”), in your Google Payments account. The card can be used to purchase eligible goods only and cannot be used to purchase Google Play devices and certain subscriptions.6- Other restrictions may apply. There are no fees or expiry dates.7- Except as required by law, the card is non-refundable or rechargeable or refundable for cash or exchangeable or cannot be merged with other Google Payments accounts in Google Play, in addition, cannot be resold or exchanged or transferred.8- The user is responsible for the loss of the card.9- For assistance or to check your card balance on Google Play Gift Code card balance, please visit: support. Google Play Gift Code card is issued by Google Arizona LLC.\"}', NULL, '2026-04-09 08:41:54', '2026-04-06 11:06:11', '2026-04-09 08:41:54'),
