then select “Payment and Purchases” and click on “Huawei Points.”4- Tap on “Redeem,” then enter the code manually or scan it to complete the top-up successfully.5- The additional 20% bonus will be added directly to your Huawei Points balance.6- Use your points for your next purchase within games and apps (except for the game Top War).7- The offer is valid only in the United Arab Emirates and Saudi Arabia.8- To receive the 20% bonus successfully, make sure you have the latest AppGallery version (12.3.0.616) and that HMS Core is properly installed.9- One (1) Huawei Point equals one (1) AED/SAR.10- You will receive a notification once the points are successfully credited.\"}', '{\"ar\": \"If the HUAWEI Points option is not displayed on the Huawei In-App Purchases screen, the app does not support HUAWEI Points.\", \"en\": \"If the HUAWEI Points option is not displayed on the Huawei In-App Purchases screen, the app does not support HUAWEI Points.\"}', NULL, '2026-04-09 08:41:54', '2026-04-06 11:06:11', '2026-04-09 08:41:54'),
(402, '61', 'like_card', '{\"ar\": \"Steam USA\", \"en\": \"Steam USA\"}', '{\"ar\": \"Steam is a digital distribution and online multiplayer platform developed by Valve Corporation.And in order to get the services of steam and all its advantages, players need to charge their account on Steam platform.With Steam USA prepaid gift cards, you can now recharge your Steam balance in order to purchase games and return to them at any time you want.Cloud storage, and software installation automatically.Voice and written chat while playing and much more of what steam platform offers.Steam cards are available at multiple prices and different packages, all you have to do is order your card, pay and receive a code to charge your account and enjoy endless benefits on Steam platform.With Steam gift Cards, playing has become more fun.\", \"en\": \"Steam is a digital distribution and online multiplayer platform developed by Valve Corporation.And in order to get the services of steam and all its advantages, players need to charge their account on Steam platform.With Steam USA prepaid gift cards, you can now recharge your Steam balance in order to purchase games and return to them at any time you want.Cloud storage, and software installation automatically.Voice and written chat while playing and much more of what steam platform offers.Steam cards are available at multiple prices and different packages, all you have to do is order your card, pay and receive a code to charge your account and enjoy endless benefits on Steam platform.With Steam gift Cards, playing has become more fun.\"}', '{\"ar\": \"How to redeem steam card:\\\\n1- Login to your Steam account.\\\\n2- Go to Redeem a Steam Wallet Code page.\\\\n3- Enter the Steam Wallet Code and click Continue.\\\\n4- The funds will be added to your account and be ready for use to buy games on STEAM!\\\\nATTENTION: This card is intended exclusively for American accounts, and therefore your account must be American so that you do not encounter any problems when trying to charge or use the card.\\\\n\", \"en\": \"How to redeem steam card:\\\\n1- Login to your Steam account.\\\\n2- Go to Redeem a Steam Wallet Code page.\\\\n3- Enter the Steam Wallet Code and click Continue.\\\\n4- The funds will be added to your account and be ready for use to buy games on STEAM!\\\\nATTENTION: This card is intended exclusively for American accounts, and therefore your account must be American so that you do not encounter any problems when trying to charge or use the card.\\\\n\"}', '{\"ar\": \"This product is for American Steam accounts.\", \"en\": \"This product is for American Steam accounts.\"}', NULL, '2026-04-09 08:41:54', '2026-04-06 11:06:11', '2026-04-09 08:41:54'),
(403, '195', 'like_card', '{\"ar\": \"UAE Steam\", \"en\": \"UAE Steam\"}', '{\"ar\": \"Steam is a digital distribution and online multiplayer platform developed by Valve Corporation.And in order to get the services of steam and all its advantages, players need to charge their account on Steam platform.With UAE Steam prepaid gift cards, you can now recharge your Steam balance in order to purchase games and return to them at any time you want.Cloud storage, and software installation automatically.Voice and written chat while playing and much more of what steam platform offers.Steam cards are available at multiple prices and different packages, all you have to do is order your card, pay and receive a code to charge your account and enjoy endless benefits on Steam platform.With Steam gift Cards, playing has become more fun.\", \"en\": \"Steam is a digital distribution and online multiplayer platform developed by Valve Corporation.And in order to get the services of steam and all its advantages, players need to charge their account on Steam platform.With UAE Steam prepaid gift cards, you can now recharge your Steam balance in order to purchase games and return to them at any time you want.Cloud storage, and software installation automatically.Voice and written chat while playing and much more of what steam platform offers.Steam cards are available at multiple prices and different packages, all you have to do is order your card, pay and receive a code to charge your account and enjoy endless benefits on Steam platform.With Steam gift Cards, playing has become more fun.\"}', '{\"ar\": \"How to redeem steam card:\\\\n1- Login to your Steam account.\\\\n2- Go to Redeem a Steam Wallet Code page.\\\\n3- Enter the Steam Wallet Code and click Continue.\\\\n4- The funds will be added to your account and be ready for use to buy games on STEAM!\\\\nATTENTION:The card currency must be matched to your Steam account currency to be able to use the product.\", \"en\": \"How to redeem steam card:\\\\n1- Login to your Steam account.\\\\n2- Go to Redeem a Steam Wallet Code page.\\\\n3- Enter the Steam Wallet Code and click Continue.\\\\n4- The funds will be added to your account and be ready for use to buy games on STEAM!\\\\nATTENTION:The card currency must be matched to your Steam account currency to be able to use the product.\"}', '{\"ar\": \"This product is for Emarati Steam accounts.\", \"en\": \"This product is for Emarati Steam accounts.\"}', NULL, '2026-04-09 08:41:54', '2026-04-06 11:06:11', '2026-04-09 08:41:54'),
(404, '358', 'like_card', '{\"ar\": \"KSA Steam\", \"en\": \"KSA Steam\"}', '{\"ar\": \"Steam is a digital distribution and online multiplayer platform developed by Valve Corporation.\\\\nAnd in order to get the services of steam and all its advantages, players need to charge their account on Steam platform.\\\\nWith KSA Steam prepaid gift cards, you can now recharge your Steam balance in order to purchase games and return to them at any time you want.\\\\nCloud storage, and software installation automatically.\\\\nVoice and written chat while playing and much more of what steam platform offers.\\\\nSteam cards are available at multiple prices and different packages, all you have to do is order your card, pay and receive a code to charge your account and enjoy endless benefits on Steam platform.\\\\nWith Steam gift Cards, playing has become more fun.\\\\n\", \"en\": \"Steam is a digital distribution and online multiplayer platform developed by Valve Corporation.\\\\nAnd in order to get the services of steam and all its advantages, players need to charge their account on Steam platform.\\\\nWith KSA Steam prepaid gift cards, you can now recharge your Steam balance in order to purchase games and return to them at any time you want.\\\\nCloud storage, and software installation automatically.\\\\nVoice and written chat while playing and much more of what steam platform offers.\\\\nSteam cards are available at multiple prices and different packages, all you have to do is order your card, pay and receive a code to charge your account and enjoy endless benefits on Steam platform.\\\\nWith Steam gift Cards, playing has become more fun.\\\\n\"}', '{\"ar\": \"How to redeem steam card:\\\\n1- Login to your Steam account.\\\\n2- Go to Redeem a Steam Wallet Code page.\\\\n3- Enter the Steam Wallet Code and click Continue.\\\\n4- The funds will be added to your account and be ready for use to buy games on STEAM!\\\\nATTENTION: The card currency must be matched to your Steam account currency to be able to use the product.\", \"en\": \"How to redeem steam card:\\\\n1- Login to your Steam account.\\\\n2- Go to Redeem a Steam Wallet Code page.\\\\n3- Enter the Steam Wallet Code and click Continue.\\\\n4- The funds will be added to your account and be ready for use to buy games on STEAM!\\\\nATTENTION: The card currency must be matched to your Steam account currency to be able to use the product.\"}', '{\"ar\": \"This product is for Saudi Steam accounts.\", \"en\": \"This product is for Saudi Steam accounts.\"}', NULL, '2026-04-09 08:41:54', '2026-04-06 11:06:11', '2026-04-09 08:41:54');
INSERT INTO `digital_merchants` (`id`, `merchant_id`, `company_name`, `name`, `description`, `redeem_steps`, `terms`, `parent_id`, `last_synced_at`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(405, '589', 'like_card', '{\"ar\": \"EUR Steam\", \"en\": \"EUR Steam\"}', '{\"ar\": \"Steam is a digital distribution and online multiplayer platform developed by Valve Corporation.And in order to get the services of steam and all its advantages, players need to charge their account on Steam platform.With EUR Steam prepaid gift cards, you can now recharge your Steam balance in order to purchase games and return to them at any time you want.Cloud storage, and software installation automatically.Voice and written chat while playing and much more of what steam platform offers.Steam cards are available at multiple prices and different packages, all you have to do is order your card, pay and receive a code to charge your account and enjoy endless benefits on Steam platform.With Steam gift Cards, playing has become more fun.\", \"en\": \"Steam is a digital distribution and online multiplayer platform developed by Valve Corporation.And in order to get the services of steam and all its advantages, players need to charge their account on Steam platform.With EUR Steam prepaid gift cards, you can now recharge your Steam balance in order to purchase games and return to them at any time you want.Cloud storage, and software installation automatically.Voice and written chat while playing and much more of what steam platform offers.Steam cards are available at multiple prices and different packages, all you have to do is order your card, pay and receive a code to charge your account and enjoy endless benefits on Steam platform.With Steam gift Cards, playing has become more fun.\"}', '{\"ar\": \"How to redeem steam card:\\\\n1- Login to your Steam account.\\\\n2- Go to Redeem a Steam Wallet Code page.\\\\n3- Enter the Steam Wallet Code and click Continue.\\\\n4- The funds will be added to your account and be ready for use to buy games on STEAM!\\\\nATTENTION:The card currency must be matched to your Steam account currency to be able to use the product.\", \"en\": \"How to redeem steam card:\\\\n1- Login to your Steam account.\\\\n2- Go to Redeem a Steam Wallet Code page.\\\\n3- Enter the Steam Wallet Code and click Continue.\\\\n4- The funds will be added to your account and be ready for use to buy games on STEAM!\\\\nATTENTION:The card currency must be matched to your Steam account currency to be able to use the product.\"}', '{\"ar\": \"This product is for European Steam accounts.\", \"en\": \"This product is for European Steam accounts.\"}', NULL, '2026-04-09 08:41:54', '2026-04-06 11:06:11', '2026-04-09 08:41:54'),
(406, '1431', 'like_card', '{\"ar\": \"Steam South Africa\", \"en\": \"Steam South Africa\"}', '{\"ar\": \"Steam is a digital distribution and online multiplayer platform developed by Valve Corporation.And in order to get the services of steam and all its advantages, players need to charge their account on Steam platform.With Steam South Africa prepaid gift cards, you can now recharge your Steam balance in order to purchase games and return to them at any time you want.Cloud storage, and software installation automatically.Voice and written chat while playing and much more of what steam platform offers.Steam cards are available at multiple prices and different packages, all you have to do is order your card, pay and receive a code to charge your account and enjoy endless benefits on Steam platform.With Steam gift Cards, playing has become more fun.\", \"en\": \"Steam is a digital distribution and online multiplayer platform developed by Valve Corporation.And in order to get the services of steam and all its advantages, players need to charge their account on Steam platform.With Steam South Africa prepaid gift cards, you can now recharge your Steam balance in order to purchase games and return to them at any time you want.Cloud storage, and software installation automatically.Voice and written chat while playing and much more of what steam platform offers.Steam cards are available at multiple prices and different packages, all you have to do is order your card, pay and receive a code to charge your account and enjoy endless benefits on Steam platform.With Steam gift Cards, playing has become more fun.\"}', '{\"ar\": \"How to redeem steam card:\\\\n1- Login to your Steam account.\\\\n2- Go to Redeem a Steam Wallet Code page.\\\\n3- Enter the Steam Wallet Code and click Continue.\\\\n4- The funds will be added to your account and be ready for use to buy games on STEAM!\\\\nATTENTION: The card currency must be matched to your Steam account currency to be able to use the product.\", \"en\": \"How to redeem steam card:\\\\n1- Login to your Steam account.\\\\n2- Go to Redeem a Steam Wallet Code page.\\\\n3- Enter the Steam Wallet Code and click Continue.\\\\n4- The funds will be added to your account and be ready for use to buy games on STEAM!\\\\nATTENTION: The card currency must be matched to your Steam account currency to be able to use the product.\"}', '{\"ar\": \"This product is for South Africa Steam accounts.\", \"en\": \"This product is for South Africa Steam accounts.\"}', NULL, '2026-04-09 08:41:54', '2026-04-06 11:06:11', '2026-04-09 08:41:54'),
(407, '1466', 'like_card', '{\"ar\": \"PSN - Turkey\", \"en\": \"PSN - Turkey\"}', '{\"ar\": \"You want to enjoy the best additions and the latest games on your Playstation?You love games, challenges and adventure in gaming?You want to have the latest features and updates from Sony store?Of Course you do, because you&apos;re a gamer.And because we think and care about you, and all gamers.We are providing you today with PSN - Turkey gift cards to charge your wallet balance, buy the latest games from Sony Store, online gameplay with millions of gamers and many additions and features that not everyone can get.With secure payment methods, our PlayStation gift cards enable you to pay safely, buy, and get all the features from Sony Store without having to use your credit card to enjoy playing.You don&apos;t have to worry anymore, buy a Playstation gift card, charge your credit and enjoy unlimited services and features, to play and have a great time.\", \"en\": \"You want to enjoy the best additions and the latest games on your Playstation?You love games, challenges and adventure in gaming?You want to have the latest features and updates from Sony store?Of Course you do, because you&apos;re a gamer.And because we think and care about you, and all gamers.We are providing you today with PSN - Turkey gift cards to charge your wallet balance, buy the latest games from Sony Store, online gameplay with millions of gamers and many additions and features that not everyone can get.With secure payment methods, our PlayStation gift cards enable you to pay safely, buy, and get all the features from Sony Store without having to use your credit card to enjoy playing.You don&apos;t have to worry anymore, buy a Playstation gift card, charge your credit and enjoy unlimited services and features, to play and have a great time.\"}', '{\"ar\": \"How to redeem PlayStation card:\\\\n1- Sign in to PlayStation Network on  PS4, PS5, PSP or PC using Media Go.\\\\n2- Head over to the PlayStation Store and select the Redeem Codes icon at the top of the page.\\\\n3- Enter your PSN card code and the money will be added to your wallet instantly.\\\\n- An illustration of how to use PlayStation cards: https://youtu.be/R4moGDIeebQ\", \"en\": \"How to redeem PlayStation card:\\\\n1- Sign in to PlayStation Network on  PS4, PS5, PSP or PC using Media Go.\\\\n2- Head over to the PlayStation Store and select the Redeem Codes icon at the top of the page.\\\\n3- Enter your PSN card code and the money will be added to your wallet instantly.\\\\n- An illustration of how to use PlayStation cards: https://youtu.be/R4moGDIeebQ\"}', '{\"ar\": \"1- Broadband, Wi-Fi or 3G internet connection required (system dependent). User is responsible for internet connection fees.\\\\n2- Code redeemable only against the issuer by users holding an SEN account registered in respective region.\\\\n3- FPB 18 users must be SEN master account holders aged 18 & over. Aged 7 & over require parental consent if under 18.\\\\n4- Online multiplayer functionality on PlayStation®4 is only available to users with a current paid-for PlayStation®Plus account.\\\\n5- Voucher code issued by Sony Interactive Entertainment Network Europe Limited and expires 12 months from date of purchase.\\\\n6- Voucher code not redeemable for cash and cannot be resold or, exchanged.\\\\n\", \"en\": \"1- Broadband, Wi-Fi or 3G internet connection required (system dependent). User is responsible for internet connection fees.\\\\n2- Code redeemable only against the issuer by users holding an SEN account registered in respective region.\\\\n3- FPB 18 users must be SEN master account holders aged 18 & over. Aged 7 & over require parental consent if under 18.\\\\n4- Online multiplayer functionality on PlayStation®4 is only available to users with a current paid-for PlayStation®Plus account.\\\\n5- Voucher code issued by Sony Interactive Entertainment Network Europe Limited and expires 12 months from date of purchase.\\\\n6- Voucher code not redeemable for cash and cannot be resold or, exchanged.\\\\n\"}', NULL, '2026-04-09 08:41:54', '2026-04-06 11:06:11', '2026-04-09 08:41:54'),
