xchanged.\"}', NULL, '2026-04-09 08:41:54', '2026-04-06 11:06:11', '2026-04-09 08:41:54'),
(413, '1681', 'like_card', '{\"ar\": \"Viking Rise\", \"en\": \"Viking Rise\"}', '{\"ar\": \"[Viking Rise] is an online multiplayer, real-time war strategy game. You play as a Viking ruler, guiding your Tribe throughout Valhalla in the uncharted world of Midgard. Explore, plunder, hunt, and fight your way across Valhalla to accrue massive wealth, fame, and power. Form alliances with other players, protect one another, and defeat all enemies to conquer Midgard!\", \"en\": \"[Viking Rise] is an online multiplayer, real-time war strategy game. You play as a Viking ruler, guiding your Tribe throughout Valhalla in the uncharted world of Midgard. Explore, plunder, hunt, and fight your way across Valhalla to accrue massive wealth, fame, and power. Form alliances with other players, protect one another, and defeat all enemies to conquer Midgard!\"}', '{\"ar\": \"How to redeem Viking Rise:1- Tap your portrait on the top left corner of the game interface.2- Go to Settings. .3- Tap Redeem Gift to enter the CODE and redeem.\", \"en\": \"How to redeem Viking Rise:1- Tap your portrait on the top left corner of the game interface.2- Go to Settings. .3- Tap Redeem Gift to enter the CODE and redeem.\"}', '{\"ar\": \"This gift card is non-refundable and cannot be exchanged for cash.This gift card cannot be reloaded.\", \"en\": \"This gift card is non-refundable and cannot be exchanged for cash.This gift card cannot be reloaded.\"}', NULL, '2026-04-09 08:41:54', '2026-04-06 11:06:11', '2026-04-09 08:41:54'),
(414, '341', 'like_card', '{\"ar\": \"Lords mobile cards\", \"en\": \"Lords mobile cards\"}', '{\"ar\": \"You play Lords Mobile?\\\\nThen you must be seeking to unite the kingdoms of Lords, and rule them with an iron fist\\\\nWith Lords mobile cards gift Cards, now you can.\\\\nGet your gift card, charge your account and enjoy all the features and advantages you need to rule.\\\\nPrepaid gift cards allow you to charge your account to purchase all resources such as wood, gold and others, in addition to weapons, characters, and all what you need to conquer your enemies.\\\\nAvailable in different balances and packages.\\\\nAll you have to do is order your card now, charge your account and build your endless empire.\\\\nWith Lords Mobile Cards, we give you the keys to defeat your enemies.\\\\n\", \"en\": \"You play Lords Mobile?\\\\nThen you must be seeking to unite the kingdoms of Lords, and rule them with an iron fist\\\\nWith Lords mobile cards gift Cards, now you can.\\\\nGet your gift card, charge your account and enjoy all the features and advantages you need to rule.\\\\nPrepaid gift cards allow you to charge your account to purchase all resources such as wood, gold and others, in addition to weapons, characters, and all what you need to conquer your enemies.\\\\nAvailable in different balances and packages.\\\\nAll you have to do is order your card now, charge your account and build your endless empire.\\\\nWith Lords Mobile Cards, we give you the keys to defeat your enemies.\\\\n\"}', '{\"ar\": \"How to redeem Lords mobile cards:\\\\n1- [Android / Steam]: Tap on [Gear] > [Redemption Code], and enter the code.\\\\n2- [iOS]: Upgrade your Castle to Lv.\\\\n3- Tap the top left icon just below the chat window to access the [Events Board] > [News] > [New Gift Code Exchange Center!]. Tap [Exchange Here] to access the Exchange Center and enter the code.\\\\n\", \"en\": \"How to redeem Lords mobile cards:\\\\n1- [Android / Steam]: Tap on [Gear] > [Redemption Code], and enter the code.\\\\n2- [iOS]: Upgrade your Castle to Lv.\\\\n3- Tap the top left icon just below the chat window to access the [Events Board] > [News] > [New Gift Code Exchange Center!]. Tap [Exchange Here] to access the Exchange Center and enter the code.\\\\n\"}', '{\"ar\": \"This product is valid for use in all countries\\\\n\", \"en\": \"This product is valid for use in all countries\\\\n\"}', NULL, '2026-04-09 08:41:54', '2026-04-06 11:06:11', '2026-04-09 08:41:54'),
(415, '1400', 'like_card', '{\"ar\": \"Candy Crush\", \"en\": \"Candy Crush\"}', '{\"ar\": \"Candy Crush is a sweet and addictive puzzle game where players match colorful candies in combinations of three or more to complete challenging levels. With its vibrant visuals, fun power-ups, and hundreds of levels, Candy Crush offers endless entertainment for casual gamers and puzzle enthusiasts alike. Swipe, match, and crush your way to victory\\\\n\", \"en\": \"Candy Crush is a sweet and addictive puzzle game where players match colorful candies in combinations of three or more to complete challenging levels. With its vibrant visuals, fun power-ups, and hundreds of levels, Candy Crush offers endless entertainment for casual gamers and puzzle enthusiasts alike. Swipe, match, and crush your way to victory\\\\n\"}', '{\"ar\": \"1- Go to http://store.king.com \\\\n2- Log in to your account or create a new account.3- Enter the code and password on the website.4- Choose the game you want to add gold bars to. Head into the game and enjoy!\", \"en\": \"1- Go to http://store.king.com \\\\n2- Log in to your account or create a new account.3- Enter the code and password on the website.4- Choose the game you want to add gold bars to. Head into the game and enjoy!\"}', '{\"ar\": \"This gift card is non-refundable and cannot be exchanged for cash.This gift card cannot be reloaded.\", \"en\": \"This gift card is non-refundable and cannot be exchanged for cash.This gift card cannot be reloaded.\"}', NULL, '2026-04-09 08:41:54', '2026-04-06 11:06:11', '2026-04-09 08:41:54'),
(416, '1809', 'like_card', '{\"ar\": \"Delta Force\", \"en\": \"Delta Force\"}', '{\"ar\": \"If you are a Delta Force player and you love to win, then you know It&apos;s a long way to survive out of 50 other fighters.\\\\nWe offer you today Delta Force gift cards to charge your account with diamonds, so you can get the best additions, the coolest costumes and skins, and the deadliest weapons to crush\\\\nyour enemies and survive.\\\\nGift cards with various offers and prices to supply your needs and charge your account with diamonds.\\\\nYou can order these cards now in a safe, quick way to develop and decorate your account.\\\\nOnce you purchase the card, you receive the code immediately that enables you to get many privileges within the game.\\\\nYou want to win. You want to look cool with deadly weapons and attractive skins. With Delta Force  cards, you can.\\\\nWhat are you waiting for then ! charge your account and conquer the world\", \"en\": \"If you are a Delta Force player and you love to win, then you know It&apos;s a long way to survive out of 50 other fighters.\\\\nWe offer you today Delta Force gift cards to charge your account with diamonds, so you can get the best additions, the coolest costumes and skins, and the deadliest weapons to crush\\\\nyour enemies and survive.\\\\nGift cards with various offers and prices to supply your needs and charge your account with diamonds.\\\\nYou can order these cards now in a safe, quick way to develop and decorate your account.\\\\nOnce you purchase the card, you receive the code immediately that enables you to get many privileges within the game.\\\\nYou want to win. You want to look cool with deadly weapons and attractive skins. With Delta Force  cards, you can.\\\\nWhat are you waiting for then ! charge your account and conquer the world\"}', '{\"ar\": \"How to redeem Delta Force Card:1- Enter the link and choose the game Delta Force:shop.garena.sg/app2-Choose the shipping method via the player ID (PLAYER ID)3- Enter your PLAYER ID and press LOG IN4 Select the Garena PPC option, then enter the code and press ConfirmHow to find Delta Force Player ID:1-Use your account to log into the game.2-Click your avatar on the top-left corner.3-Your Delta Force Player ID will be displayed.\", \"en\": \"How to redeem Delta Force Card:1- Enter the link and choose the game Delta Force:shop.garena.sg/app2-Choose the shipping method via the player ID (PLAYER ID)3- Enter your PLAYER ID and press LOG IN4 Select the Garena PPC option, then enter the code and press ConfirmHow to find Delta Force Player ID:1-Use your account to log into the game.2-Click your avatar on the top-left corner.3-Your Delta Force Player ID will be displayed.\"}', '{\"ar\": \"This product is valid for use in all countries\", \"en\": \"This product is valid for use in all countries\"}', NULL, '2026-04-09 08:41:54', '2026-04-06 11:06:11', '2026-04-09 08:41:54'),
(417, '261', 'like_card', '{\"ar\": \"Roblox\", \"en\": \"Roblox\"}', '{\"ar\": \"Roblox is one of the most popular online games, allowing millions of players around the world to explore and build virtual worlds, with their own characters, in addition to collecting objects, clothes, materials, and so much more.\\\\nRoblox Prepaid gift cards allow you to charge your account on Roblox, in order to purchase and buy everything you need as a player within the world of Roblox, including clothes, add-ons, games, characters and unlocking new worlds.\\\\nRoblox cards with multiple prices, and different packages to suit all players.\\\\nOrder your card, pay in completely secure ways and get a card that allows you to charge your account on Roblox to enjoy an exceptional experience on Roblox.\\\\n\", \"en\": \"Roblox is one of the most popular online games, allowing millions of players around the world to explore and build virtual worlds, with their own characters, in addition to collecting objects, clothes, materials, and so much more.\\\\nRoblox Prepaid gift cards allow you to charge your account on Roblox, in order to purchase and buy everything you need as a player within the world of Roblox, including clothes, add-ons, games, characters and unlocking new worlds.\\\\nRoblox cards with multiple prices, and different packages to suit all players.\\\\nOrder your card, pay in completely secure ways and get a card that allows you to charge your account on Roblox to enjoy an exceptional experience on Roblox.\\\\n\"}', '{\"ar\": \"1- Log in to the Roblox account on which you want to redeem the code.\\\\n2- Go to the redeem code page ( https://www.roblox.com/gamecards/redeem )\\\\n3- Enter the code number that you got.\\\\n4- Click on “Redeem”.\\\\n\", \"en\": \"1- Log in to the Roblox account on which you want to redeem the code.\\\\n2- Go to the redeem code page ( https://www.roblox.com/gamecards/redeem )\\\\n3- Enter the code number that you got.\\\\n4- Click on “Redeem”.\\\\n\"}', '{\"ar\": \"- The currency of the card must match the currency of your Roblox account in order to be able to use the product.\\\\n\", \"en\": \"- The currency of the card must match the currency of your Roblox account in order to be able to use the product.\\\\n\"}', NULL, '2026-04-09 08:41:54', '2026-04-06 11:06:11', '2026-04-09 08:41:54'),
(418, '593', 'like_card', '{\"ar\": \"USA Roblox\", \"en\": \"USA Roblox\"}', '{\"ar\": \"-Get more with every Roblox Gift Card! From now on, when you redeem a Roblox Gift Card, you get up to 25% more Robux. Perfect for gaming, creating, and exploring- more Robux means more possibilities!-Roblox Gift Cards can only be redeemed in a browser at https://Roblox.com/They cannot be redeemed in the Roblox mobile app or any video game console.-Deck out your avatar and unlock additional perks in your favorite experiences when you use Roblox Gift Cards to purchase Robux (Roblox&apos;s virtual currency).-Get exclusive access to virtual items, a monthly Robux stipend, and more by redeeming your gift card for a Roblox Premium subscription. -Each gift card grants a free virtual item upon redemption.\", \"en\": \"-Get more with every Roblox Gift Card! From now on, when you redeem a Roblox Gift Card, you get up to 25% more Robux. Perfect for gaming, creating, and exploring- more Robux means more possibilities!-Roblox Gift Cards can only be redeemed in a browser at https://Roblox.com/They cannot be redeemed in the Roblox mobile app or any video game console.-Deck out your avatar and unlock additional perks in your favorite experiences when you use Roblox Gift Cards to purchase Robux (Roblox&apos;s virtual currency).-Get exclusive access to virtual items, a monthly Robux stipend, and more by redeeming your gift card for a Roblox Premium subscription. -Each gift card grants a free virtual item upon redemption.\"}', '{\"ar\": \"1- Go to Roblox.com/Redeem from your browse2- Log in or create an account3- Find your PIN and enter it on the website4- Spend your credit on Robux or a Roblox Premium subscription\", \"en\": \"1- Go to Roblox.com/Redeem from your browse2- Log in or create an account3- Find your PIN and enter it on the website4- Spend your credit on Robux or a Roblox Premium subscription\"}', '{\"ar\": \"1- By purchasing or using this card, you or your parent or guardian agree to these terms and the Roblox Terms of Use at roblox.com (see roblox.com/termsofuse), which are both subject to change.2- This card may only be redeemed at roblox.com for Roblox credits, which are only redeemable for Robux or a Roblox Premium Subscription.3- Redemption of credits for Robux may be subject to applicable sales tax.4- Roblox may also award a bonus of up to 25% more Robux upon redemption of credits, depending on amount of Robux purchased.5- Not refundable or redeemable for cash, except as required by law.6- To redeem this card, you must have a Roblox account.7- This card is issued by and represents an obligation solely of Roblox Prepaid Company, LLC.8- For complete terms and conditions including arbitration agreement and class action waiver, visit roblox.com/giftcardterms.9- ©2025 Roblox Corporation. All rights reserved.10- Roblox, Robux, and the Roblox Tilt logo are trademarks of Roblox Corporation.\", \"en\": \"1- By purchasing or using this card, you or your parent or guardian agree to these terms and the Roblox Terms of Use at roblox.com (see roblox.com/termsofuse), which are both subject to change.2- This card may only be redeemed at roblox.com for Roblox credits, which are only redeemable for Robux or a Roblox Premium Subscription.3- Redemption of credits for Robux may be subject to applicable sales tax.4- Roblox may also award a bonus of up to 25% more Robux upon redemption of credits, depending on amount of Robux purchased.5- Not refundable or redeemable for cash, except as required by law.6- To redeem this card, you must have a Roblox account.7- This card is issued by and represents an obligation solely of Roblox Prepaid Company, LLC.8- For complete terms and conditions including arbitration agreement and class action waiver, visit roblox.com/giftcardterms.9- ©2025 Roblox Corporation. All rights reserved.10- Roblox, Robux, and the Roblox Tilt logo are trademarks of Roblox Corporation.\"}', 417, '2026-04-09 08:41:54', '2026-04-06 11:06:11', '2026-04-09 08:41:54'),
(419, '594', 'like_card', '{\"ar\": \"EUR Roblox\", \"en\": \"EUR Roblox\"}', '{\"ar\": \"Purchase Roblox gift cards to obtain Robux in-game credit or maximize the fun with a Premium Membership. With Robux Credit, you can purchase additional content for your favourite games and new items for your character!\", \"en\": \"Purchase Roblox gift cards to obtain Robux in-game credit or maximize the fun with a Premium Membership. With Robux Credit, you can purchase additional content for your favourite games and new items for your character!\"}', '{\"ar\": \"1- Log in to the Roblox account on which you want to redeem the code.\\\\n2- Go to the redeem code page ( https://www.roblox.com/gamecards/redeem )\\\\n3- Enter the code number that you got.\\\\n4- Click on “Redeem”.\\\\n\", \"en\": \"1- Log in to the Roblox account on which you want to redeem the code.\\\\n2- Go to the redeem code page ( https://www.roblox.com/gamecards/redeem )\\\\n3- Enter the code number that you got.\\\\n4- Click on “Redeem”.\\\\n\"}', '{\"ar\": \"- To view the terms and conditions please visit: https://www.roblox.com/gamecards/redeem\", \"en\": \"- To view the terms and conditions please visit: https://www.roblox.com/gamecards/redeem\"}', 417, '2026-04-09 08:41:54', '2026-04-06 11:06:11', '2026-04-09 08:41:54'),
(420, '1494', 'like_card', '{\"ar\": \"KSA Roblox\", \"en\": \"KSA Roblox\"}', '{\"ar\": \"Roblox is an immersive platform for connection and communication. Every day, millions of people come to Roblox to create, play, work, learn, and connect with each other in experiences built by our global community of creators.\", \"en\": \"Roblox is an immersive platform for connection and communication. Every day, millions of people come to Roblox to create, play, work, learn, and connect with each other in experiences built by our global community of creators.\"}', '{\"ar\": \"Redemption: Online only. Roblox Gift Cards can only be redeemed in a browser at Roblox.com/redeem. The gift cards can&apos;t be redeemed in the Roblox mobile app or any video game console.\", \"en\": \"Redemption: Online only. Roblox Gift Cards can only be redeemed in a browser at Roblox.com/redeem. The gift cards can&apos;t be redeemed in the Roblox mobile app or any video game console.\"}', '{\"ar\": \"1- By purchasing, accepting or redeeming this card, you (or your parent or guardian if you are under 18 years old) agree to these terms and conditions and the Roblox Terms of Use (available at www.roblox.com/termsofuse), which are both subject to change.2- This card may only be redeemed at www.roblox.com for Roblox credits,3- which may only be used to purchase Robux or a Roblox Premium Subscription4- (availability and pricing are subject to change — see https://www.roblox.com/upgrades/robux).5- This card is not refundable or redeemable for cash, except as required by law.6- To redeem this card and use Roblox credits, you must have Internet access and register for a Roblox account.7- Resale is prohibited.8- Roblox is not responsible if this card is used without your permission or if it is lost, stolen or damaged.9- This card is issued by and represents an obligation solely of Roblox Prepaid Company, LLC.10- For the complete terms and conditions including the arbitration agreement and class action waiver, please visit www.roblox.com/giftcardterms.\", \"en\": \"1- By purchasing, accepting or redeeming this card, you (or your parent or guardian if you are under 18 years old) agree to these terms and conditions and the Roblox Terms of Use (available at www.roblox.com/termsofuse), which are both subject to change.2- This card may only be redeemed at www.roblox.com for Roblox credits,3- which may only be used to purchase Robux or a Roblox Premium Subscription4- (availability and pricing are subject to change — see https://www.roblox.com/upgrades/robux).5- This card is not refundable or redeemable for cash, except as required by law.6- To redeem this card and use Roblox credits, you must have Internet access and register for a Roblox account.7- Resale is prohibited.8- Roblox is not responsible if this card is used without your permission or if it is lost, stolen or damaged.9- This card is issued by and represents an obligation solely of Roblox Prepaid Company, LLC.10- For the complete terms and conditions including the arbitration agreement and class action waiver, please visit www.roblox.com/giftcardterms.\"}', 417, '2026-04-09 08:41:54', '2026-04-06 11:06:11', '2026-04-09 08:41:54');
