(437, '1265', 'like_card', '{\"ar\": \"The Lord of The Rings\", \"en\": \"The Lord of The Rings\"}', '{\"ar\": \"The Lord of the Rings: Rise to War, a mobile strategy and war game, is published by NetEase Games and Warner Bros. Interactive. Build your strongest army of Frodo, Aragorn, Gandalf and other iconic heroes in the battle for Middle-earth in this mobile strategy and war game with Turkish language support and strategically expand your territory around the ring.\", \"en\": \"The Lord of the Rings: Rise to War, a mobile strategy and war game, is published by NetEase Games and Warner Bros. Interactive. Build your strongest army of Frodo, Aragorn, Gandalf and other iconic heroes in the battle for Middle-earth in this mobile strategy and war game with Turkish language support and strategically expand your territory around the ring.\"}', '{\"ar\": \"How to use The Lord of the Rings cards:To redeem the code you purchased from LikeCard, follow the steps below:1- Open GamesClub On the page that opens, select the game you want to install.2- Select \\\"NetEase Pay,\\\" then select the server and enter your user ID. Select the package you want to purchase and proceed with the \\\"Top-Up\\\" button.3- On the page that opens, enter the codes you purchased from LikeCard.\", \"en\": \"How to use The Lord of the Rings cards:To redeem the code you purchased from LikeCard, follow the steps below:1- Open GamesClub On the page that opens, select the game you want to install.2- Select \\\"NetEase Pay,\\\" then select the server and enter your user ID. Select the package you want to purchase and proceed with the \\\"Top-Up\\\" button.3- On the page that opens, enter the codes you purchased from LikeCard.\"}', '{\"ar\": \"1- Valid on global servers.2- This code is not valid in Thailand, Malaysia, Singapore, Indonesia, Myanmar, and Laos.3- Products are delivered instantly as an e-pin after payment is completed.4- Digital products cannot be returned in accordance with the relevant article of the Turkish Commercial Code.\", \"en\": \"1- Valid on global servers.2- This code is not valid in Thailand, Malaysia, Singapore, Indonesia, Myanmar, and Laos.3- Products are delivered instantly as an e-pin after payment is completed.4- Digital products cannot be returned in accordance with the relevant article of the Turkish Commercial Code.\"}', NULL, '2026-04-09 08:41:54', '2026-04-06 11:06:11', '2026-04-09 08:41:54'),
(438, '1386', 'like_card', '{\"ar\": \"Overwatch 2\", \"en\": \"Overwatch 2\"}', '{\"ar\": \"A free-to-play shooter featuring 30+ epic heroes, each with game-changing abilities. Choose the hero, group up with your friends, and battle across all-new maps and modes in the ultimate team-based shooter.\", \"en\": \"A free-to-play shooter featuring 30+ epic heroes, each with game-changing abilities. Choose the hero, group up with your friends, and battle across all-new maps and modes in the ultimate team-based shooter.\"}', '{\"ar\": \"Steps to Redeem on the Xbox Website:1- Go to the Microsoft Redeem Page:Open a web browser and navigate to redeem.microsoft.com2- Sign In:Log in with your Microsoft account that is linked to your Xbox profile.3- Enter the Code:In the text box, type your 25-character code.You don&apos;t need to include the dashes as they’ll be automatically formatted.4- Click “Next”:After entering the code, click the Next button to proceed.5- Confirm Redemption:Follow any additional prompts to confirm the redemption. The value or content should now be added to your account.Additional Tips:- Verify the Account: Ensure you&apos;re logged into the correct account to avoid redeeming the code on the wrong profile.- Check Redemption Details: After redeeming, the content will either appear in your library (for games/content) or your account balance will be updated (for gift cards).- Troubleshooting: If the code doesn&apos;t work, double-check for typos, ensure the code hasn&apos;t already been redeemed, and verify it matches your region.\", \"en\": \"Steps to Redeem on the Xbox Website:1- Go to the Microsoft Redeem Page:Open a web browser and navigate to redeem.microsoft.com2- Sign In:Log in with your Microsoft account that is linked to your Xbox profile.3- Enter the Code:In the text box, type your 25-character code.You don&apos;t need to include the dashes as they’ll be automatically formatted.4- Click “Next”:After entering the code, click the Next button to proceed.5- Confirm Redemption:Follow any additional prompts to confirm the redemption. The value or content should now be added to your account.Additional Tips:- Verify the Account: Ensure you&apos;re logged into the correct account to avoid redeeming the code on the wrong profile.- Check Redemption Details: After redeeming, the content will either appear in your library (for games/content) or your account balance will be updated (for gift cards).- Troubleshooting: If the code doesn&apos;t work, double-check for typos, ensure the code hasn&apos;t already been redeemed, and verify it matches your region.\"}', '{\"ar\": \"- This gift card is non-refundable and cannot be exchanged for cash.- This gift card cannot be reloaded.\", \"en\": \"- This gift card is non-refundable and cannot be exchanged for cash.- This gift card cannot be reloaded.\"}', NULL, '2026-04-09 08:41:54', '2026-04-06 11:06:11', '2026-04-09 08:41:54'),
(439, '1705', 'like_card', '{\"ar\": \"Vikingard\", \"en\": \"Vikingard\"}', '{\"ar\": \"Achieve unmatched victories and showcase your leadership to the world! Fight for land, harvest your resources, make critical choices, and join a Viking-spirited battle with fellow warriors! With powerful characters, a captivating storyline, thrilling events, rewarding gameplay, and dynamic design, VIKINGARD is a masterpiece every gamer should experience.\", \"en\": \"Achieve unmatched victories and showcase your leadership to the world! Fight for land, harvest your resources, make critical choices, and join a Viking-spirited battle with fellow warriors! With powerful characters, a captivating storyline, thrilling events, rewarding gameplay, and dynamic design, VIKINGARD is a masterpiece every gamer should experience.\"}', '{\"ar\": \"To activate your Gift Card Voucher please follow the below steps:• Go to https://pay.neteasegames.com/ • Select your game server• Enter your ID• Enter the code and select the “Continue” button• Enter your serial number (Redeem code)• Enter the “Activate” button\", \"en\": \"To activate your Gift Card Voucher please follow the below steps:• Go to https://pay.neteasegames.com/ • Select your game server• Enter your ID• Enter the code and select the “Continue” button• Enter your serial number (Redeem code)• Enter the “Activate” button\"}', '{\"ar\": \"1-  Valid for 10 years. 2-  Once purchased, cannot be returned or refunded\", \"en\": \"1-  Valid for 10 years. 2-  Once purchased, cannot be returned or refunded\"}', NULL, '2026-04-09 08:41:54', '2026-04-06 11:06:11', '2026-04-09 08:41:54'),
(440, '1268', 'like_card', '{\"ar\": \"Point Blank TG - TRY\", \"en\": \"Point Blank TG - TRY\"}', '{\"ar\": \"Point Blank, developed by the South Korean gaming company Zepetto and released in October 2008, is an online first-person shooter. It is published in Türkiye by Nfinity Games.The game centers on the war between CT-Forces and Free Rebels.You can purchase various weapons and ammunition with TG, the in-game currency. PB TG gives you access to special in-game store content and allows your character to progress faster and become one of the best in the game.\", \"en\": \"Point Blank, developed by the South Korean gaming company Zepetto and released in October 2008, is an online first-person shooter. It is published in Türkiye by Nfinity Games.The game centers on the war between CT-Forces and Free Rebels.You can purchase various weapons and ammunition with TG, the in-game currency. PB TG gives you access to special in-game store content and allows your character to progress faster and become one of the best in the game.\"}', '{\"ar\": \"How to use Point Blank cards:To use the Point Black code you purchased from LikeCard, follow the steps below:1- Click the \\\"Sign In\\\" tab atpb.tamgame.com .2- Log in by entering your membership information.3- Click the \\\"I Want to Load TG\\\" button.4- Select E-Pin as your payment method and click the \\\"Continue\\\" button.5- On the page that opens, enter the code you purchased from LikeCard and click the \\\"Continue\\\" button.\", \"en\": \"How to use Point Blank cards:To use the Point Black code you purchased from LikeCard, follow the steps below:1- Click the \\\"Sign In\\\" tab atpb.tamgame.com .2- Log in by entering your membership information.3- Click the \\\"I Want to Load TG\\\" button.4- Select E-Pin as your payment method and click the \\\"Continue\\\" button.5- On the page that opens, enter the code you purchased from LikeCard and click the \\\"Continue\\\" button.\"}', '{\"ar\": \"1- Valid in Turkey.2- Products are delivered instantly as an e-pin after payment is completed.3- Digital products cannot be returned in accordance with the relevant article of the Turkish Commercial Code.\", \"en\": \"1- Valid in Turkey.2- Products are delivered instantly as an e-pin after payment is completed.3- Digital products cannot be returned in accordance with the relevant article of the Turkish Commercial Code.\"}', NULL, '2026-04-09 08:41:54', '2026-04-06 11:06:11', '2026-04-09 08:41:54'),
(441, '110', 'like_card', '{\"ar\": \"Game Stop\", \"en\": \"Game Stop\"}', '{\"ar\": \"You can use GameStop Cards to purchase products from US GameStop stores.\\\\n\", \"en\": \"You can use GameStop Cards to purchase products from US GameStop stores.\\\\n\"}', '{\"ar\": \"1- Enter the link: wbiprod.storedvalue.com/wbir/clients/gamestop\\\\n2- Enter the card code and the PIN code that you got.\\\\n3- Press CHECK BALANCE\\\\n\", \"en\": \"1- Enter the link: wbiprod.storedvalue.com/wbir/clients/gamestop\\\\n2- Enter the card code and the PIN code that you got.\\\\n3- Press CHECK BALANCE\\\\n\"}', '{\"ar\": \"Terms & Conditions of checkout using Game Stop gift card:\\\\n1- Not applicable to purchase digital goods such as Steam gift card, Google gift card and more outside the United States.\\\\n2- The item must be physical.\\\\n3- The item must be in-stock (No pre-order).\\\\n4- Only can use up to 2 gift cards to check out in one single purchase.\\\\n5- You&apos;re required to be logged in at the time of the transaction.\\\\n\", \"en\": \"Terms & Conditions of checkout using Game Stop gift card:\\\\n1- Not applicable to purchase digital goods such as Steam gift card, Google gift card and more outside the United States.\\\\n2- The item must be physical.\\\\n3- The item must be in-stock (No pre-order).\\\\n4- Only can use up to 2 gift cards to check out in one single purchase.\\\\n5- You&apos;re required to be logged in at the time of the transaction.\\\\n\"}', NULL, '2026-04-09 08:41:54', '2026-04-06 11:06:11', '2026-04-09 08:41:54'),
(442, '675', 'like_card', '{\"ar\": \"Genshin Impact\", \"en\": \"Genshin Impact\"}', '{\"ar\": \"a free-to-play, open-world action RPG, It features a vast, explorable world called Teyvat, divided into seven nations, each with its own unique culture and associated element. \", \"en\": \"a free-to-play, open-world action RPG, It features a vast, explorable world called Teyvat, divided into seven nations, each with its own unique culture and associated element. \"}', '{\"ar\": \"How to redeem Genshin Impact cards:\\\\n1- Enter the game and copy the game (ID).\\\\n2- Enter the application or website.\\\\n3- Enter the required data and then proceed with the purchase process.\\\\n\", \"en\": \"How to redeem Genshin Impact cards:\\\\n1- Enter the game and copy the game (ID).\\\\n2- Enter the application or website.\\\\n3- Enter the required data and then proceed with the purchase process.\\\\n\"}', '{\"ar\": \"- This product is valid for use in all countries\", \"en\": \"- This product is valid for use in all countries\"}', NULL, '2026-04-09 08:41:54', '2026-04-06 11:06:11', '2026-04-09 08:41:54'),
(443, '1191', 'like_card', '{\"ar\": \"Xbox Games\", \"en\": \"Xbox Games\"}', '{\"ar\": \"Xbox Games offer a vast library of immersive experiences, from action-packed adventures to competitive multiplayer battles and captivating story-driven journeys. With cutting-edge graphics, innovative gameplay, and exclusive titles, Xbox delivers unforgettable moments for gamers of all types. Whether you&apos;re playing solo or teaming up online, the world of Xbox Games is your gateway to endless fun and excitement.\", \"en\": \"Xbox Games offer a vast library of immersive experiences, from action-packed adventures to competitive multiplayer battles and captivating story-driven journeys. With cutting-edge graphics, innovative gameplay, and exclusive titles, Xbox delivers unforgettable moments for gamers of all types. Whether you&apos;re playing solo or teaming up online, the world of Xbox Games is your gateway to endless fun and excitement.\"}', '{\"ar\": \"- How to redeem the card using your Xbox Series X|S or Xbox One:1- Press the Xbox button to open the guide, then select Store.2- Click on the offer button to open the side menu, then select Redeem.3- Enter the 25-character code, select Next, then follow the instructions.\\\\n- How to redeem the card using your Xbox 360:1- Press the Guide button on your controller.2- Select Games & Apps, then select Redeem Code.3- Enter the 25-character code, select Next, then follow the instructions.- How to redeem the card using a PC or mobile web browser:1- Enter the link: https://redeem.microsoft.com/ 2- Enter the code you obtained, then follow the instructions.- How to redeem the card using Microsoft Store on Windows:1- Press the Start menu button, then enter store in the search box.2- Choose Microsoft Store from the results to open the application.3- Select your account in the upper left corner of the screen, then select Redeem Code or Gift Cards.4- Enter the 25-character code, select Next, then follow the instructions.\", \"en\": \"- How to redeem the card using your Xbox Series X|S or Xbox One:1- Press the Xbox button to open the guide, then select Store.2- Click on the offer button to open the side menu, then select Redeem.3- Enter the 25-character code, select Next, then follow the instructions.\\\\n- How to redeem the card using your Xbox 360:1- Press the Guide button on your controller.2- Select Games & Apps, then select Redeem Code.3- Enter the 25-character code, select Next, then follow the instructions.- How to redeem the card using a PC or mobile web browser:1- Enter the link: https://redeem.microsoft.com/ 2- Enter the code you obtained, then follow the instructions.- How to redeem the card using Microsoft Store on Windows:1- Press the Start menu button, then enter store in the search box.2- Choose Microsoft Store from the results to open the application.3- Select your account in the upper left corner of the screen, then select Redeem Code or Gift Cards.4- Enter the 25-character code, select Next, then follow the instructions.\"}', '{\"ar\": \"- To know the terms and conditions, go to: www.microsoft.com/en/servicesagreement \", \"en\": \"- To know the terms and conditions, go to: www.microsoft.com/en/servicesagreement \"}', NULL, '2026-04-09 08:41:54', '2026-04-06 11:06:11', '2026-04-09 08:41:54'),
(444, '1205', 'like_card', '{\"ar\": \"Steam Games\", \"en\": \"Steam Games\"}', '{\"ar\": \" Steam Games bring a world of gaming at your fingertips, featuring a massive collection of titles across every genre imaginable. From indie gems to blockbuster hits, the platform offers something for everyone. Enjoy seamless downloads, regular updates, community features, and exclusive sales. Whether you&apos;re into strategy, action, RPGs, or VR, Steam Games delivers endless entertainment for every kind of gamer.\", \"en\": \" Steam Games bring a world of gaming at your fingertips, featuring a massive collection of titles across every genre imaginable. From indie gems to blockbuster hits, the platform offers something for everyone. Enjoy seamless downloads, regular updates, community features, and exclusive sales. Whether you&apos;re into strategy, action, RPGs, or VR, Steam Games delivers endless entertainment for every kind of gamer.\"}', '{\"ar\": \"1- Download and installed the &apos;Steam Client&apos; on your computer.2- Run the Steam Client.3- Create an account on Steam (or login if you already have one)4- Activate your purchased key(s) into your Steam account and install the game.\", \"en\": \"1- Download and installed the &apos;Steam Client&apos; on your computer.2- Run the Steam Client.3- Create an account on Steam (or login if you already have one)4- Activate your purchased key(s) into your Steam account and install the game.\"}', '{\"ar\": \"1- Please be careful when selecting the regional code you wish to buy. Once the code leaves our secure inventory, we can no longer guarantee the validity of the code; therefore, after an order has been sent we cannot return or exchange it.2- Codes have a 3 (three) year validity from the date of purchase.3- Code will not be replaced by the brand or your retailer if the card is lost or stolen.4- Code cannot be exchanged for cash. \", \"en\": \"1- Please be careful when selecting the regional code you wish to buy. Once the code leaves our secure inventory, we can no longer guarantee the validity of the code; therefore, after an order has been sent we cannot return or exchange it.2- Codes have a 3 (three) year validity from the date of purchase.3- Code will not be replaced by the brand or your retailer if the card is lost or stolen.4- Code cannot be exchanged for cash. \"}', NULL, '2026-04-09 08:41:54', '2026-04-06 11:06:11', '2026-04-09 08:41:54');
