ce.\\\\n5- Choose to pay with gift cards.\\\\n6- Enter the card code that you got.\\\\n7- Click on apply to your balance.\\\\n\"}', '{\"ar\": \"- This product is for Saudi amazon accounts.\", \"en\": \"- This product is for Saudi amazon accounts.\"}', NULL, '2026-04-09 08:41:54', '2026-04-06 11:06:11', '2026-04-09 08:41:54'),
(448, '123', 'like_card', '{\"ar\": \"NetFlix USA\", \"en\": \"NetFlix USA\"}', '{\"ar\": \"If you have a passion for movies, and you admire cinema and artwork then you must be familiar with Netflix.With over than 200 million subscribers around the world, Netflix is one of the largest companies specialized in producing movies and TV shows.With NetFlix USA , you can enjoy various shows, movies, series, entertainment programs, and documentaries from some of the world&apos;s most powerful production studios.High quality, translation, and unlimited entertainment content.All you have to do is buy a Netflix gift card and enjoy your favorite shows, movies and series.Cards with different packages and prices.Safe and easy Payment methods, so you get the code immediately after payment.Come on then, get your Netflix gift cards and enjoy your time.\\\\n\", \"en\": \"If you have a passion for movies, and you admire cinema and artwork then you must be familiar with Netflix.With over than 200 million subscribers around the world, Netflix is one of the largest companies specialized in producing movies and TV shows.With NetFlix USA , you can enjoy various shows, movies, series, entertainment programs, and documentaries from some of the world&apos;s most powerful production studios.High quality, translation, and unlimited entertainment content.All you have to do is buy a Netflix gift card and enjoy your favorite shows, movies and series.Cards with different packages and prices.Safe and easy Payment methods, so you get the code immediately after payment.Come on then, get your Netflix gift cards and enjoy your time.\\\\n\"}', '{\"ar\": \"How to redeem netflix card:\\\\n1- Enter the following link: https://bit.ly/netflixcomredeem\\\\n2- Add your email and click Continue\\\\n3- If you do not have an account, click on Create Account\\\\n4- Add an email and password and click Continue\\\\n5- Create an account by clicking Continue\\\\n6- Click See The Plans to view subscriptions\\\\n7- Check the price and features and then select the category that suits you\\\\n8- Click on Continue\\\\n9- Subscription is activated, press Start Membership\\\\n10- Add the phone number, then press Continue\\\\nATTENTION: This card is intended exclusively for American accounts, and therefore your account must be American so that you do not encounter any problems when trying to charge or use the card.\\\\n\", \"en\": \"How to redeem netflix card:\\\\n1- Enter the following link: https://bit.ly/netflixcomredeem\\\\n2- Add your email and click Continue\\\\n3- If you do not have an account, click on Create Account\\\\n4- Add an email and password and click Continue\\\\n5- Create an account by clicking Continue\\\\n6- Click See The Plans to view subscriptions\\\\n7- Check the price and features and then select the category that suits you\\\\n8- Click on Continue\\\\n9- Subscription is activated, press Start Membership\\\\n10- Add the phone number, then press Continue\\\\nATTENTION: This card is intended exclusively for American accounts, and therefore your account must be American so that you do not encounter any problems when trying to charge or use the card.\\\\n\"}', '{\"ar\": \"1- Valid only towards the Netflix service via Netflix account (18+ or age of majority to become a member), in the of  American .\\\\n2- Entire value credited to your Netflix account upon redemption.\\\\n3- Nonrefundable and not redeemable for cash, except where required by law.\\\\n4- Does not expire. No resale.\\\\n5- Netflix is not responsible for lost or stolen cards or unauthorized use.\\\\n6- Full terms apply, visit: www.netflix.com/cardterms .Cards issued by Netflix International B.V.\", \"en\": \"1- Valid only towards the Netflix service via Netflix account (18+ or age of majority to become a member), in the of  American .\\\\n2- Entire value credited to your Netflix account upon redemption.\\\\n3- Nonrefundable and not redeemable for cash, except where required by law.\\\\n4- Does not expire. No resale.\\\\n5- Netflix is not responsible for lost or stolen cards or unauthorized use.\\\\n6- Full terms apply, visit: www.netflix.com/cardterms .Cards issued by Netflix International B.V.\"}', NULL, '2026-04-09 08:41:54', '2026-04-06 11:06:11', '2026-04-09 08:41:54'),
(449, '1278', 'like_card', '{\"ar\": \"Netflix - TRY\", \"en\": \"Netflix - TRY\"}', '{\"ar\": \"If you have a passion for movies, and you admire cinema and artwork then you must be familiar with Netflix.With over than 200 million subscribers around the world, Netflix is one of the largest companies specialized in producing movies and TV shows.With Netflix - TRY , you can enjoy various shows, movies, series, entertainment programs, and documentaries from some of the world&apos;s most powerful production studios.High quality, translation, and unlimited entertainment content.All you have to do is buy a Netflix gift card and enjoy your favorite shows, movies and series.Cards with different packages and prices.Safe and easy Payment methods, so you get the code immediately after payment.Come on then, get your Netflix gift cards and enjoy your time.\", \"en\": \"If you have a passion for movies, and you admire cinema and artwork then you must be familiar with Netflix.With over than 200 million subscribers around the world, Netflix is one of the largest companies specialized in producing movies and TV shows.With Netflix - TRY , you can enjoy various shows, movies, series, entertainment programs, and documentaries from some of the world&apos;s most powerful production studios.High quality, translation, and unlimited entertainment content.All you have to do is buy a Netflix gift card and enjoy your favorite shows, movies and series.Cards with different packages and prices.Safe and easy Payment methods, so you get the code immediately after payment.Come on then, get your Netflix gift cards and enjoy your time.\"}', '{\"ar\": \"How to redeem netflix card:\\\\n1- Enter the following link https://bit.ly/netflixcomredeem\\\\n2- Add your email and click Continue\\\\n3- If you do not have an account, click on Create Account\\\\n4- Add an email and password and click Continue\\\\n5- Create an account by clicking Continue\\\\n6- Click See The Plans to view subscriptions\\\\n7- Check the price and features and then select the category that suits you\\\\n8- Click on Continue\\\\n9- Subscription is activated, press Start Membership\\\\n10- Add the phone number, then press Continue\", \"en\": \"How to redeem netflix card:\\\\n1- Enter the following link https://bit.ly/netflixcomredeem\\\\n2- Add your email and click Continue\\\\n3- If you do not have an account, click on Create Account\\\\n4- Add an email and password and click Continue\\\\n5- Create an account by clicking Continue\\\\n6- Click See The Plans to view subscriptions\\\\n7- Check the price and features and then select the category that suits you\\\\n8- Click on Continue\\\\n9- Subscription is activated, press Start Membership\\\\n10- Add the phone number, then press Continue\"}', '{\"ar\": \"1- Valid only towards the Netflix service via Netflix account (18+ or age of majority to become a member), in the Kingdom of Saudi Arabia.\\\\n2- Entire value credited to your Netflix account upon redemption.\\\\n3- Nonrefundable and not redeemable for cash, except where required by law.\\\\n4- Does not expire. No resale.\\\\n5- Netflix is not responsible for lost or stolen cards or unauthorized use.\\\\n6- Full terms apply, visit: www.netflix.com/cardterms .Cards issued by Netflix International B.V.\", \"en\": \"1- Valid only towards the Netflix service via Netflix account (18+ or age of majority to become a member), in the Kingdom of Saudi Arabia.\\\\n2- Entire value credited to your Netflix account upon redemption.\\\\n3- Nonrefundable and not redeemable for cash, except where required by law.\\\\n4- Does not expire. No resale.\\\\n5- Netflix is not responsible for lost or stolen cards or unauthorized use.\\\\n6- Full terms apply, visit: www.netflix.com/cardterms .Cards issued by Netflix International B.V.\"}', NULL, '2026-04-09 08:41:54', '2026-04-06 11:06:11', '2026-04-09 08:41:54'),
(450, '987', 'like_card', '{\"ar\": \"Deezer\", \"en\": \"Deezer\"}', '{\"ar\": \"Deezer is an online music streaming service. It allows users to listen to music content from record labels, including Universal Music Group, Sony Music and Warner Music Group as well as podcasts on various devices online or offline.\", \"en\": \"Deezer is an online music streaming service. It allows users to listen to music content from record labels, including Universal Music Group, Sony Music and Warner Music Group as well as podcasts on various devices online or offline.\"}', '{\"ar\": \"How to redeem Deezer Cards:\\\\n1- Enter the Store: www.deezer.com/gift\\\\n2- Enter the card code that you got from Like Card.\\\\n3- Click on Submit.\\\\n\", \"en\": \"How to redeem Deezer Cards:\\\\n1- Enter the Store: www.deezer.com/gift\\\\n2- Enter the card code that you got from Like Card.\\\\n3- Click on Submit.\\\\n\"}', '{\"ar\": \"- This gift card is non-refundable and cannot be exchanged for cash.- This gift card cannot be reloaded.- Expires in 1 year from date of purchase.\", \"en\": \"- This gift card is non-refundable and cannot be exchanged for cash.- This gift card cannot be reloaded.- Expires in 1 year from date of purchase.\"}', NULL, '2026-04-09 08:41:54', '2026-04-06 11:06:11', '2026-04-09 08:41:54'),
(451, '1919', 'like_card', '{\"ar\": \"Noorplay\", \"en\": \"Noorplay\"}', '{\"ar\": \"Noorplay offers safe, family-oriented entertainment that respects social and cultural values. From premium Turkish dramas to movies, kids’ shows, and animations, the platform delivers a unique viewing experience for the entire family.\", \"en\": \"Noorplay offers safe, family-oriented entertainment that respects social and cultural values. From premium Turkish dramas to movies, kids’ shows, and animations, the platform delivers a unique viewing experience for the entire family.\"}', '{\"ar\": \"1- Visit: https://www.noorplay.com/en/voucher2- Enter the voucher code to subscribe.3- Enter your email and password or create a new account.4- Enjoy NoorPlay&apos;s service.\", \"en\": \"1- Visit: https://www.noorplay.com/en/voucher2- Enter the voucher code to subscribe.3- Enter your email and password or create a new account.4- Enjoy NoorPlay&apos;s service.\"}', '{\"ar\": \"To view the terms and conditions, please visit:  https://noorplay.com/en/termsofuse\", \"en\": \"To view the terms and conditions, please visit:  https://noorplay.com/en/termsofuse\"}', NULL, '2026-04-09 08:41:54', '2026-04-06 11:06:11', '2026-04-09 08:41:54'),
