t Apps, and select the Store app from there.)\\\\n3- In the Store app, move the cursor left or press the View button to open the side menu then select redeem.\\\\n4- Enter the 25-character code, and then follow the instructions.\\\\nRedeem a code Using an Android or IOS mobile device:\\\\n1- Go to the link: https://redeem.microsoft.com.\\\\n2- Enter the 25-character code, and then follow the instructions.\\\\nRedeem a code on Windows 10/11:\\\\n1-Sign in to your Windows device (make sure you’re signed in with the Microsoft account you want to redeem the code with).\\\\n2-Press the Start button, type store, then select Microsoft Store.\\\\n3-Select More … > Redeem a code.\\\\n4-Enter the 25-character code, and then follow the instructions.\\\\n\"}', NULL, '2026-04-09 08:41:54', '2026-04-06 11:06:11', '2026-04-09 08:41:54'),
(481, '1209', 'like_card', '{\"ar\": \"Call Of Duty XBOX\", \"en\": \"Call Of Duty XBOX\"}', '{\"ar\": \"Call of Duty is a video game series and media franchise published by Activision, The games were first developed by Infinity Ward, then by Treyarch and Sledgehammer Games.\", \"en\": \"Call of Duty is a video game series and media franchise published by Activision, The games were first developed by Infinity Ward, then by Treyarch and Sledgehammer Games.\"}', '{\"ar\": \"How to redeem the card using your Xbox Series X|S or Xbox One:\\\\n1- Press the Xbox button to open the guide, then select Store.\\\\n2- Click on the offer button to open the side menu, then select Redeem.\\\\n3- Enter the 25-character code, select Next, then follow the instructions.\\\\nHow to redeem the card using your Xbox 360:\\\\n1- Press the Guide button on your controller.\\\\n2- Select Games & Apps, then select Redeem Code.\\\\n3- Enter the 25-character code, select Next, then follow the instructions.\\\\nHow to redeem the card using a PC or mobile web browser:\\\\n1- Enter the link: https://redeem.microsoft.com/\\\\n2- Enter the code you obtained, then follow the instructions.\\\\nHow to redeem the card using Microsoft Store on Windows:\\\\n1- Press the Start menu button, then enter store in the search box.\\\\n2- Choose Microsoft Store from the results to open the application.\\\\n3- Select your account in the upper left corner of the screen, then select Redeem Code or Gift Cards.\\\\n4- Enter the 25-character code, select Next, then follow the instructions.\\\\n\", \"en\": \"How to redeem the card using your Xbox Series X|S or Xbox One:\\\\n1- Press the Xbox button to open the guide, then select Store.\\\\n2- Click on the offer button to open the side menu, then select Redeem.\\\\n3- Enter the 25-character code, select Next, then follow the instructions.\\\\nHow to redeem the card using your Xbox 360:\\\\n1- Press the Guide button on your controller.\\\\n2- Select Games & Apps, then select Redeem Code.\\\\n3- Enter the 25-character code, select Next, then follow the instructions.\\\\nHow to redeem the card using a PC or mobile web browser:\\\\n1- Enter the link: https://redeem.microsoft.com/\\\\n2- Enter the code you obtained, then follow the instructions.\\\\nHow to redeem the card using Microsoft Store on Windows:\\\\n1- Press the Start menu button, then enter store in the search box.\\\\n2- Choose Microsoft Store from the results to open the application.\\\\n3- Select your account in the upper left corner of the screen, then select Redeem Code or Gift Cards.\\\\n4- Enter the 25-character code, select Next, then follow the instructions.\\\\n\"}', '{\"ar\": \"1- These cards are valid for the following Call Of Duty versions:\\\\nCall of Duty®: Modern Warfare® II\\\\nCall of Duty®: Modern Warfare®\\\\nCall of Duty®: Vanguard\\\\nCall of Duty®: Black Ops Cold War\\\\nCall of Duty®: Warzone™ 2.0\\\\n2- To view the terms and conditions, please visit:\\\\nhttps://www.microsoft.com/ar/servicesagreement/\\\\n\", \"en\": \"1- These cards are valid for the following Call Of Duty versions:\\\\nCall of Duty®: Modern Warfare® II\\\\nCall of Duty®: Modern Warfare®\\\\nCall of Duty®: Vanguard\\\\nCall of Duty®: Black Ops Cold War\\\\nCall of Duty®: Warzone™ 2.0\\\\n2- To view the terms and conditions, please visit:\\\\nhttps://www.microsoft.com/ar/servicesagreement/\\\\n\"}', NULL, '2026-04-09 08:41:54', '2026-04-06 11:06:11', '2026-04-09 08:41:54'),
(482, '1233', 'like_card', '{\"ar\": \"EA FC Mobile Silver\", \"en\": \"EA FC Mobile Silver\"}', '{\"ar\": \"EA SPORTS FC™ is here—the next chapter in The World&apos;s Game. Join us in building the future of football on a foundation of innovation and authenticity with more than 19,000 fully licensed players, 700 teams, and 30 leagues. Created for fans by fans, EA SPORTS FC is a new Football Club for the future of football we want to build together.\\\\nSilver: can be used to buy in-game items such as Star Pass & Welcome Bundles.\\\\nSilver Store: can be accessed from the in-game store under the Silver Category.\\\\nEnjoy getting additional free points with every card.\\\\n\", \"en\": \"EA SPORTS FC™ is here—the next chapter in The World&apos;s Game. Join us in building the future of football on a foundation of innovation and authenticity with more than 19,000 fully licensed players, 700 teams, and 30 leagues. Created for fans by fans, EA SPORTS FC is a new Football Club for the future of football we want to build together.\\\\nSilver: can be used to buy in-game items such as Star Pass & Welcome Bundles.\\\\nSilver Store: can be accessed from the in-game store under the Silver Category.\\\\nEnjoy getting additional free points with every card.\\\\n\"}', '{\"ar\": \"How to redeem EA FC Mobile Silver cards:\\\\n1- Enter the link: redeem.meplay.com/game/eafc/\\\\n2- Select EAFC game and Click on the REDEEM CODE tab.\\\\n3- If you are not a member register first, by logging in with your account.\\\\n4- Type in your Player ID and Code, then click Redeem.\\\\n5- Once you’ve redeemed your code, will appear in your account.\\\\n\", \"en\": \"How to redeem EA FC Mobile Silver cards:\\\\n1- Enter the link: redeem.meplay.com/game/eafc/\\\\n2- Select EAFC game and Click on the REDEEM CODE tab.\\\\n3- If you are not a member register first, by logging in with your account.\\\\n4- Type in your Player ID and Code, then click Redeem.\\\\n5- Once you’ve redeemed your code, will appear in your account.\\\\n\"}', '{\"ar\": \"1- Available on Android and iOS.\\\\n2- Age Rating 12+\\\\n3- Your use of this card is subject to the requirements printed on the card.\\\\n4- This cards full terms and conditions are available at https://redeem.meplay.com/game/eafc. By purchasing, using or accepting this card you agree to all such requirements, full terms and conditions.\\\\n5- Please note, FC Silver and FC Silver Accounts are region specific, which means you can only use the FC Silver codes specific to the region you have opened an account from. For example, if you have opened an account in Brazil, you can only purchase Brazil specific FC Silver Points for that region/country.\\\\n6- Once you have loaded your FC Silver onto your account you are ready to play.\\\\n7- Please be careful when selecting the regional code you wish to buy. Once a FC Silver Digital code leaves our secure inventory, we can no longer guarantee the validity of the code; therefore, after an order has been sent we cannot return or exchange it.\\\\n8- FC Silver Codes have a 1 (one) year validity from date of purchase.\\\\n\", \"en\": \"1- Available on Android and iOS.\\\\n2- Age Rating 12+\\\\n3- Your use of this card is subject to the requirements printed on the card.\\\\n4- This cards full terms and conditions are available at https://redeem.meplay.com/game/eafc. By purchasing, using or accepting this card you agree to all such requirements, full terms and conditions.\\\\n5- Please note, FC Silver and FC Silver Accounts are region specific, which means you can only use the FC Silver codes specific to the region you have opened an account from. For example, if you have opened an account in Brazil, you can only purchase Brazil specific FC Silver Points for that region/country.\\\\n6- Once you have loaded your FC Silver onto your account you are ready to play.\\\\n7- Please be careful when selecting the regional code you wish to buy. Once a FC Silver Digital code leaves our secure inventory, we can no longer guarantee the validity of the code; therefore, after an order has been sent we cannot return or exchange it.\\\\n8- FC Silver Codes have a 1 (one) year validity from date of purchase.\\\\n\"}', NULL, '2026-04-09 08:41:54', '2026-04-06 11:06:11', '2026-04-09 08:41:54');
