our secure inventory, we can no longer guarantee the validity of the code; therefore, after an order has been sent we cannot return or exchange it.\\\\n8- FC Silver Codes have a 1 (one) year validity from date of purchase.\\\\n\"}', 482, '2026-04-09 08:41:54', '2026-04-06 11:06:11', '2026-04-09 08:41:54'),
(484, '1122', 'like_card', '{\"ar\": \"EA FC Mobile POINTS\", \"en\": \"EA FC Mobile POINTS\"}', '{\"ar\": \"Play through well known global tournaments with qualified and non qualified national teams. Train Football heroes- Train your favourite players increasing their stats and moving them to the next level! Fast Game, Exciting goals- Score goals with the world best players using creative modes. Build momentum with precision passing-Dominate possession with new ways to pass, open up space and create attacking opportunities.\\\\n\", \"en\": \"Play through well known global tournaments with qualified and non qualified national teams. Train Football heroes- Train your favourite players increasing their stats and moving them to the next level! Fast Game, Exciting goals- Score goals with the world best players using creative modes. Build momentum with precision passing-Dominate possession with new ways to pass, open up space and create attacking opportunities.\\\\n\"}', '{\"ar\": \"How to redeem EA FC Mobile Points card:\\\\n1- Enter the link: redeem.meplay.com/game/eafc/\\\\n2- Select EAFC game and Click on the REDEEM CODE tab.\\\\n3- If you are not a member register first, by logging in with your account.\\\\n4- Type in your Player ID and Code, then click Redeem.\\\\n5- Once you’ve redeemed your code, will appear in your account.\\\\n\", \"en\": \"How to redeem EA FC Mobile Points card:\\\\n1- Enter the link: redeem.meplay.com/game/eafc/\\\\n2- Select EAFC game and Click on the REDEEM CODE tab.\\\\n3- If you are not a member register first, by logging in with your account.\\\\n4- Type in your Player ID and Code, then click Redeem.\\\\n5- Once you’ve redeemed your code, will appear in your account.\\\\n\"}', '{\"ar\": \"1- Available on Android and iOS.\\\\n2- Age Rating 12+\\\\n3- Your use of this card is subject to the requirements printed on the card.\\\\n4- This cards full terms and conditions are available at https://redeem.meplay.com/game/eafc. By purchasing, usin