rchasing, using or accepting this card you agree to all such requirements, full terms and conditions.\\\\n5- Please note, FC Silver and FC Silver Accounts are region specific, which means you can only use the FC Silver codes specific to the region you have opened an account from. For example, if you have opened an account in Brazil, you can only purchase Brazil specific FC Silver Points for that region/country.\\\\n6- Once you have loaded your FC Silver onto your account you are ready to play.\\\\n7- Please be careful when selecting the regional code you wish to buy. Once a FC Silver Digital code leaves our secure inventory, we can no longer guarantee the validity of the code; therefore, after an order has been sent we cannot return or exchange it.\\\\n8- FC Silver Codes have a 1 (one) year validity from date of purchase.\", \"en\": \"1- Available on Android and iOS.\\\\n2- Age Rating 12+\\\\n3- Your use of this card is subject to the requirements printed on the card.\\\\n4- This cards full terms and conditions are available at https://redeem.meplay.com/game/eafc. By purchasing, using or accepting this card you agree to all such requirements, full terms and conditions.\\\\n5- Please note, FC Silver and FC Silver Accounts are region specific, which means you can only use the FC Silver codes specific to the region you have opened an account from. For example, if you have opened an account in Brazil, you can only purchase Brazil specific FC Silver Points for that region/country.\\\\n6- Once you have loaded your FC Silver onto your account you are ready to play.\\\\n7- Please be careful when selecting the regional code you wish to buy. Once a FC Silver Digital code leaves our secure inventory, we can no longer guarantee the validity of the code; therefore, after an order has been sent we cannot return or exchange it.\\\\n8- FC Silver Codes have a 1 (one) year validity from date of purchase.\"}', 484, '2026-04-09 08:41:54', '2026-04-06 11:06:11', '2026-04-09 08:41:54'),
(486, '591', 'like_card', '{\"ar\": \"USA Nintendo\", \"en\": \"USA Nintendo\"}', '{\"ar\": \"Nintendo gift cards are prepaid cards that allow you to charge your account on Nintendo to enjoy games, products and all the features on Nintendo Store.\\\\nIf you are into gaming, and a fan of Nintendo you don&apos;t have to worry anymore. we are providing you with prepaid Nintendo gift cards so you can buy all the exclusive games, and the new products from Nintendo and so much more.\\\\nCards at different prices and packages.\\\\nUnlimited use.\\\\nPayment in safe ways with immediate delivery.\\\\nOrder your card, pay and enjoy in the world of Nintendo games.\\\\n\", \"en\": \"Nintendo gift cards are prepaid cards that allow you to charge your account on Nintendo to enjoy games, products and all the features on Nintendo Store.\\\\nIf you are into gaming, and a fan of Nintendo you don&apos;t have to worry anymore. we are providing you with prepaid Nintendo gift cards so you can buy all the exclusive games, and the new products from Nintendo and so much more.\\\\nCards at different prices and packages.\\\\nUnlimited use.\\\\nPayment in safe ways with immediate delivery.\\\\nOrder your card, pay and enjoy in the world of Nintendo games.\\\\n\"}', '{\"ar\": \"How to redeem Nintendo Shop cards:\\\\n1- Select the Nintendo eShop icon in the HOME menu.\\\\n2- Scroll to the left and select \\\"Add funds\\\".\\\\n3- Select Nintendo eShop Card Redeem.\\\\n4- Enter the code number that you got.\\\\n5- Select “OK” to complete the transaction.\\\\nATTENTION: This card is intended exclusively for American accounts, and therefore your account must be American so that you do not encounter any problems when trying to charge or use the card.\\\\n\", \"en\": \"How to redeem Nintendo Shop cards:\\\\n1- Select the Nintendo eShop icon in the HOME menu.\\\\n2- Scroll to the left and select \\\"Add funds\\\".\\\\n3- Select Nintendo eShop Card Redeem.\\\\n4- Enter the code number that you got.\\\\n5- Select “OK” to complete the transaction.\\\\nATTENTION: This card is intended exclusively for American accounts, and therefore your account must be American so that you do not encounter any problems when trying to charge or use the card.\\\\n\"}', '{\"ar\": \"This product is for American nintendo accounts\\\\n\", \"en\": \"This product is for American nintendo accounts\\\\n\"}', NULL, '2026-04-09 08:41:54', '2026-04-06 11:06:11', '2026-04-09 08:41:54'),
(487, '592', 'like_card', '{\"ar\": \"EUR Nintendo\", \"en\": \"EUR Nintendo\"}', '{\"ar\": \"Nintendo  gift cards are prepaid cards that allow you to charge your account on Nintendo to enjoy games, products and all the features on Nintendo Store.If you are into gaming, and a fan of Nintendo you don&apos;t have to worry anymore. we are providing you with prepaid Nintendo gift cards so you can buy all the exclusive games, and the new products from Nintendo and so much more.Cards at different prices and packages.Unlimited use.Payment in safe ways with immediate delivery.Order your card, pay and enjoy in the world of Nintendo games.\", \"en\": \"Nintendo  gift cards are prepaid cards that allow you to charge your account on Nintendo to enjoy games, products and all the features on Nintendo Store.If you are into gaming, and a fan of Nintendo you don&apos;t have to worry anymore. we are providing you with prepaid Nintendo gift cards so you can buy all the exclusive games, and the new products from Nintendo and so much more.Cards at different prices and packages.Unlimited use.Payment in safe ways with immediate delivery.Order your card, pay and enjoy in the world of Nintendo games.\"}', '{\"ar\": \"How to charge Nintendo Shop cards:\\\\n1- Select the Nintendo eShop icon in the HOME menu.\\\\n2- Scroll to the left and select \\\"Add funds\\\".\\\\n3- Select Nintendo eShop Card Redeem.\\\\n4- Enter the code number that you got.\\\\n5- Select “OK” to complete the transaction.\\\\n\", \"en\": \"How to charge Nintendo Shop cards:\\\\n1- Select the Nintendo eShop icon in the HOME menu.\\\\n2- Scroll to the left and select \\\"Add funds\\\".\\\\n3- Select Nintendo eShop Card Redeem.\\\\n4- Enter the code number that you got.\\\\n5- Select “OK” to complete the transaction.\\\\n\"}', '{\"ar\": \"This product is for European nintendo accounts\", \"en\": \"This product is for European nintendo accounts\"}', NULL, '2026-04-09 08:41:54', '2026-04-06 11:06:11', '2026-04-09 08:41:54'),
(488, '1393', 'like_card', '{\"ar\": \"Japan Nintendo\", \"en\": \"Japan Nintendo\"}', '{\"ar\": \"Nintendo gift cards are prepaid cards that allow you to charge your account on Nintendo to enjoy games, products and all the features on Nintendo Store.If you are into gaming, and a fan of Nintendo you don&apos;t have to worry anymore. we are providing you with prepaid Nintendo gift cards so you can buy all the exclusive games, and the new products from Nintendo and so much more.Cards at different prices and packages.Unlimited use.Payment in safe ways with immediate delivery.Order your card, pay and enjoy in the world of Nintendo games.\", \"en\": \"Nintendo gift cards are prepaid cards that allow you to charge your account on Nintendo to enjoy games, products and all the features on Nintendo Store.If you are into gaming, and a fan of Nintendo you don&apos;t have to worry anymore. we are providing you with prepaid Nintendo gift cards so you can buy all the exclusive games, and the new products from Nintendo and so much more.Cards at different prices and packages.Unlimited use.Payment in safe ways with immediate delivery.Order your card, pay and enjoy in the world of Nintendo games.\"}', '{\"ar\": \"How to charge Nintendo Shop cards:\\\\n1- Select the Nintendo eShop icon in the HOME menu.\\\\n2- Scroll to the left and select \\\"Add funds\\\".\\\\n3- Select Nintendo eShop Card Redeem.\\\\n4- Enter the code number that you got.\\\\n5- Select “OK” to complete the transaction.\", \"en\": \"How to charge Nintendo Shop cards:\\\\n1- Select the Nintendo eShop icon in the HOME menu.\\\\n2- Scroll to the left and select \\\"Add funds\\\".\\\\n3- Select Nintendo eShop Card Redeem.\\\\n4- Enter the code number that you got.\\\\n5- Select “OK” to complete the transaction.\"}', '{\"ar\": \"This product is for Japanese Nintendo accounts\", \"en\": \"This product is for Japanese Nintendo accounts\"}', NULL, '2026-04-09 08:41:54', '2026-04-06 11:06:11', '2026-04-09 08:41:54'),
(489, '307', 'like_card', '{\"ar\": \"Razer USA\", \"en\": \"Razer USA\"}', '{\"ar\": \"Razer gift cards are virtual currency purchase cards supported by Razer company, that are used to purchase entertainment content such as games, as they support more than 2000 games, including PUBG, Cross fire and others, in addition to many applications such as twitch, BIGO live and many additions.\\\\nRazer USA are available in various different packages and varying prices to suit the needs of all players.\\\\nTo enjoy a perfect gaming experience, application subscriptions and more, Razer Card is the perfect solution.\\\\nAll you have to do is order and purchase the card to receive an instant code and then charge your account.\\\\nWith Razer gift Cards, fun is just one step away.\\\\n\", \"en\": \"Razer gift cards are virtual currency purchase cards supported by Razer company, that are used to purchase entertainment content such as games, as they support more than 2000 games, including PUBG, Cross fire and others, in addition to many applications such as twitch, BIGO live and many additions.\\\\nRazer USA are available in various different packages and varying prices to suit the needs of all players.\\\\nTo enjoy a perfect gaming experience, application subscriptions and more, Razer Card is the perfect solution.\\\\nAll you have to do is order and purchase the card to receive an instant code and then charge your account.\\\\nWith Razer gift Cards, fun is just one step away.\\\\n\"}', '{\"ar\": \"How to redeem Razer Card:\\\\n1- Log in to: https://gold.razer.com\\\\n2- Log in to your Razer gold account using your Razer email and password.\\\\n3- In the top menu click on Gold then click on “Reload now” and choose the Razer Gold PIN.\\\\n4- Enter the card code that you got, then press NEXT.\\\\n5- Enter the verification code sent to your phone, then press Confirm.\\\\n6- If you did not enter your number previously, you can complete the process by pressing “Set Up TFA”.\\\\n7- Enter the verification code you received via e-mail\\\\n8- You will see a message that the code has been shipped successfully, and a receipt will be sent to your e-mail.\\\\n\", \"en\": \"How to redeem Razer Card:\\\\n1- Log in to: https://gold.razer.com\\\\n2- Log in to your Razer gold account using your Razer email and password.\\\\n3- In the top menu click on Gold then click on “Reload now” and choose the Razer Gold PIN.\\\\n4- Enter the card code that you got, then press NEXT.\\\\n5- Enter the verification code sent to your phone, then press Confirm.\\\\n6- If you did not enter your number previously, you can complete the process by pressing “Set Up TFA”.\\\\n7- Enter the verification code you received via e-mail\\\\n8- You will see a message that the code has been shipped successfully, and a receipt will be sent to your e-mail.\\\\n\"}', '{\"ar\": \"This product is for American razer accounts\\\\n\", \"en\": \"This product is for American razer accounts\\\\n\"}', NULL, '2026-04-09 08:41:54', '2026-04-06 11:06:11', '2026-04-09 08:41:54'),
(490, '308', 'like_card', '{\"ar\": \"Razer Global\", \"en\": \"Razer Global\"}', '{\"ar\": \"Razer gift cards are virtual currency purchase cards supported by Razer company, that are used to purchase entertainment content such as games, as they support more than 2000 games, including PUBG, Cross fire and others, in addition to many applications such as twitch, BIGO live and many additions.Razer Global are available in various different packages and varying prices to suit the needs of all players.To enjoy a perfect gaming experience, application subscriptions and more, Razer Card is the perfect solution.All you have to do is order and purchase the card to receive an instant code and then charge your account.With Razer gift Cards, fun is just one step away.\", \"en\": \"Razer gift cards are virtual currency purchase cards supported by Razer company, that are used to purchase entertainment content such as games, as they support more than 2000 games, including PUBG, Cross fire and others, in addition to many applications such as twitch, BIGO live and many additions.Razer Global are available in various different packages and varying prices to suit the needs of all players.To enjoy a perfect gaming experience, application subscriptions and more, Razer Card is the perfect solution.All you have to do is order and purchase the card to receive an instant code and then charge your account.With Razer gift Cards, fun is just one step away.\"}', '{\"ar\": \"How to redeem Razer Card:\\\\n1- Log in to: https://gold.razer.com\\\\n2- Log in to your Razer gold account using your Razer email and password.\\\\n3- In the top menu click on Gold then click on “Reload now” and choose the Razer Gold PIN.\\\\n4- Enter the card code that you got, then press NEXT.\\\\n5- Enter the verification code sent to your phone, then press Confirm.\\\\n6- If you did not enter your number previously, you can complete the process by pressing “Set Up TFA”.\\\\n7- Enter the verification code you received via e-mail\\\\n8- You will see a message that the code has been shipped successfully, and a receipt will be sent to your e-mail.\\\\n\", \"en\": \"How to redeem Razer Card:\\\\n1- Log in to: https://gold.razer.com\\\\n2- Log in to your Razer gold account using your Razer email and password.\\\\n3- In the top menu click on Gold then click on “Reload now” and choose the Razer Gold PIN.\\\\n4- Enter the card code that you got, then press NEXT.\\\\n5- Enter the verification code sent to your phone, then press Confirm.\\\\n6- If you did not enter your number previously, you can complete the process by pressing “Set Up TFA”.\\\\n7- Enter the verification code you received via e-mail\\\\n8- You will see a message that the code has been shipped successfully, and a receipt will be sent to your e-mail.\\\\n\"}', '{\"ar\": \"This product is for Global razer accounts\", \"en\": \"This product is for Global razer accounts\"}', NULL, '2026-04-09 08:41:54', '2026-04-06 11:06:11', '2026-04-09 08:41:54'),
(491, '1277', 'like_card', '{\"ar\": \"Razer TURKEY\", \"en\": \"Razer TURKEY\"}', '{\"ar\": \"Razer gift cards are virtual currency purchase cards supported by Razer company, that are used to purchase entertainment content such as games, as they support more than 2000 games, including PUBG, Cross fire and others, in addition to many applications such as twitch, BIGO live and many additions.Razer TURKEY are available in various different packages and varying prices to suit the needs of all players.To enjoy a perfect gaming experience, application subscriptions and more, Razer Card is the perfect solution.All you have to do is order and purchase the card to receive an instant code and then charge your account.With Razer gift Cards, fun is just one step away.\", \"en\": \"Razer gift cards are virtual currency purchase cards supported by Razer company, that are used to purchase entertainment content such as games, as they support more than 2000 games, including PUBG, Cross fire and others, in addition to many applications such as twitch, BIGO live and many additions.Razer TURKEY are available in various different packages and varying prices to suit the needs of all players.To enjoy a perfect gaming experience, application subscriptions and more, Razer Card is the perfect solution.All you have to do is order and purchase the card to receive an instant code and then charge your account.With Razer gift Cards, fun is just one step away.\"}', '{\"ar\": \"How to redeem Razer Card:1- Log in to: https://gold.razer.com 2- Log in to your Razer gold account using your Razer email and password.3- In the top menu click on Gold then click on â€œReload nowâ€ and choose the Razer Gold PIN.4- Enter the card code that you got, then press NEXT.5- Enter the verification code sent to your phone, then press Confirm.6- If you did not enter your number previously, you can complete the process by pressing â€œSet Up TFAâ€.7- Enter the verification code you received via e-mail8- You will see a message that the code has been shipped successfully, and a receipt will be sent to your e-mail.\", \"en\": \"How to redeem Razer Card:1- Log in to: https://gold.razer.com 2- Log in to your Razer gold account using your Razer email and password.3- In the top menu click on Gold then click on â€œReload nowâ€ and choose the Razer Gold PIN.4- Enter the card code that you got, then press NEXT.5- Enter the verification code sent to your phone, then press Confirm.6- If you did not enter your number previously, you can complete the process by pressing â€œSet Up TFAâ€.7- Enter the verification code you received via e-mail8- You will see a message that the code has been shipped successfully, and a receipt will be sent to your e-mail.\"}', '{\"ar\": \"- This gift card is non-refundable and cannot be exchanged for cash.- This gift card cannot be reloaded.\", \"en\": \"- This gift card is non-refundable and cannot be exchanged for cash.- This gift card cannot be reloaded.\"}', NULL, '2026-04-09 08:41:54', '2026-04-06 11:06:11', '2026-04-09 08:41:54'),
(492, '614', 'like_card', '{\"ar\": \"LikeCard - IRAQ\", \"en\": \"LikeCard - IRAQ\"}', '{\"ar\": \"A digital card designed to help you effortlessly recharge your balance on the LikeCard app. You can also share it as a thoughtful gift with family and friends, giving them the convenience of easily choosing their favorite card directly from the app.\\\\n\", \"en\": \"A digital card designed to help you effortlessly recharge your balance on the LikeCard app. You can also share it as a thoughtful gift with family and friends, giving them the convenience of easily choosing their favorite card directly from the app.\\\\n\"}', '{\"ar\": \"How to redeem LikeCard cards:\\\\n1- Open the LikeCard app and log in to your account.2- From the bottom menu, select  Account  .3- Under your LikeCard balance, tap Recharge.4- In the “Recharge Card Balance” section, choose Redeem Code.5- Enter your unique gift card code and press Redeem Code to complete the process.\", \"en\": \"How to redeem LikeCard cards:\\\\n1- Open the LikeCard app and log in to your account.2- From the bottom menu, select  Account  .3- Under your LikeCard balance, tap Recharge.4- In the “Recharge Card Balance” section, choose Redeem Code.5- Enter your unique gift card code and press Redeem Code to complete the process.\"}', '{\"ar\": \"1- This card is valid for 12 months from the date of purchase.\\\\n2- The currency of the card must be matched to the currency of your store in LikeCard in order to be able to use the product.\\\\n\", \"en\": \"1- This card is valid for 12 months from the date of purchase.\\\\n2- The currency of the card must be matched to the currency of your store in LikeCard in order to be able to use the product.\\\\n\"}', NULL, '2026-04-09 08:41:54', '2026-04-06 11:06:11', '2026-04-09 08:41:54'),
